'''自噬'''（{{lang-en|Autophagy}}，或稱'''自體吞噬'''）是一個涉及到[[細胞|細胞]]自身結構通過[[溶酶體|溶酶體]]機制，負責將受損的細胞器、錯誤折疊的蛋白及其他大分子物質等運送至溶酶體降解並再利用的進化保守過程。自噬是廣泛存在於真核細胞的現象，並且可分為巨自噬、微自噬和分子伴侶介導的自噬三大類。這是一個受到緊密調控的步驟，此步驟是細胞生長、[[細胞分化|發育]]與[[穩態|穩態]]中的常規步驟，幫助細胞產物在合成、降解以及接下來的循環中保持一個平衡狀態。目前已有多份研究表明自噬在許多細胞的分化進程中被不同程度地觸發<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Guan |first1=JL |last2=Simon |first2=AK |last3=Prescott |first3=M |last4=Menendez |first4=JA |last5=Liu |first5=F |last6=Wang |first6=F |last7=Wang |first7=C |last8=Wolvetang |first8=E |last9=Vazquez-Martin |first9=A |last10=Zhang |first10=J |title=Autophagy in stem cells. |journal=Autophagy |date=2013-06-01 |volume=9 |issue=6 |pages=830-49 |doi=10.4161/auto.24132 |pmid=23486312 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23486312-autophagy-in-stem-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>，例如參與血管生成<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Torisu |first1=T |last2=Torisu |first2=K |last3=Lee |first3=IH |last4=Liu |first4=J |last5=Malide |first5=D |last6=Combs |first6=CA |last7=Wu |first7=XS |last8=Rovira |first8=II |last9=Fergusson |first9=MM |last10=Weigert |first10=R |last11=Connelly |first11=PS |last12=Daniels |first12=MP |last13=Komatsu |first13=M |last14=Cao |first14=L |last15=Finkel |first15=T |title=Autophagy regulates endothelial cell processing, maturation and secretion of von Willebrand factor. |journal=Nature medicine |date=2013-10 |volume=19 |issue=10 |pages=1281-7 |doi=10.1038/nm.3288 |pmid=24056772 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24056772-autophagy-regulates-endothelial-cell-processing-maturation-and-secretion-of-von-willebrand-factor/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>、成骨分化<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Pantovic |first1=A |last2=Krstic |first2=A |last3=Janjetovic |first3=K |last4=Kocic |first4=J |last5=Harhaji-Trajkovic |first5=L |last6=Bugarski |first6=D |last7=Trajkovic |first7=V |title=Coordinated time-dependent modulation of AMPK/Akt/mTOR signaling and autophagy controls osteogenic differentiation of human mesenchymal stem cells. |journal=Bone |date=2013-01 |volume=52 |issue=1 |pages=524-31 |doi=10.1016/j.bone.2012.10.024 |pmid=23111315 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23111315-coordinated-time-dependent-modulation-of-ampkaktmtor-signaling-and-autophagy-controls-osteogenic-differentiation-of-human-mesenchymal-stem-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>、脂肪生成<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nuschke |first1=A |last2=Rodrigues |first2=M |last3=Stolz |first3=DB |last4=Chu |first4=CT |last5=Griffith |first5=L |last6=Wells |first6=A |title=Human mesenchymal stem cells/multipotent stromal cells consume accumulated autophagosomes early in differentiation. |journal=Stem cell research & therapy |date=2014-12-17 |volume=5 |issue=6 |pages=140 |doi=10.1186/scrt530 |pmid=25523618 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25523618-human-mesenchymal-stem-cellsmultipotent-stromal-cells-consume-accumulated-autophagosomes-early-in-differentiation/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>、神經發生<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Vázquez |first1=P |last2=Arroba |first2=AI |last3=Cecconi |first3=F |last4=de la Rosa |first4=EJ |last5=Boya |first5=P |last6=de Pablo |first6=F |title=Atg5 and Ambra1 differentially modulate neurogenesis in neural stem cells. |journal=Autophagy |date=2012-02-01 |volume=8 |issue=2 |pages=187-99 |doi=10.4161/auto.8.2.18535 |pmid=22240590 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22240590-atg5-and-ambra1-differentially-modulate-neurogenesis-in-neural-stem-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>等過程。

自噬效應的發生取決於自噬流過程是否完成，而自噬流的意思是自噬的完整動態過程，包括自噬體形成、自噬體與溶酶體融合及後續內含物的降解和回收<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lu |first1=Y |last2=Dong |first2=S |last3=Hao |first3=B |last4=Li |first4=C |last5=Zhu |first5=K |last6=Guo |first6=W |last7=Wang |first7=Q |last8=Cheung |first8=KH |last9=Wong |first9=CW |last10=Wu |first10=WT |last11=Markus |first11=H |last12=Yue |first12=J |title=Vacuolin-1 potently and reversibly inhibits autophagosome-lysosome fusion by activating RAB5A. |journal=Autophagy |date=2014 |volume=10 |issue=11 |pages=1895-905 |doi=10.4161/auto.32200 |pmid=25483964 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25483964-vacuolin-1-potently-and-reversibly-inhibits-autophagosome-lysosome-fusion-by-activating-rab5a/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>。

命名為“自噬”（{{lang-en|Autophagy}}）是由比利時化學家[[克里斯汀·德·迪夫|克里斯汀·德·迪夫]]在1963年發現的<ref name=klionsky>{{cite journal |pmid= 18567941 |year= 2008 |last1= Klionsky |first1= DJ |title= Autophagy revisited: A conversation with Christian de Duve |volume= 4 |issue= 6 |pages= 740–3 |journal= Autophagy |doi=10.4161/auto.6398}}</ref>。當代的自噬研究是1990年代酵母的研究人員通過識別的自噬相關基因而被推動<ref name="klionsky 1992">{{cite journal|pmid=1400574|title=Aminopeptidase I of Saccharomyces cerevisiae is localized to the vacuole independent of the secretory pathway|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1992-10_119_2/page/287|journal=Journal of Cell Biology|date=October 1992|volume=119|issue=2|page=287-99|}}</ref><ref name="ohsumi 1992">{{cite journal|pmid=1400575|title=Autophagy in yeast demonstrated with proteinase-deficient mutants and conditions for its induction|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1992-10_119_2/page/301|journal=Journal of Cell Biology|date=October 1992|volume=119|issue=2|page=301-11|}}</ref><ref name="thumm 1994">{{cite journal|title=Isolation of autophagocytosis mutants of Saccharomyces cerevisiae|journal=FEBS Letters|date=August 1994|volume=349|issue=2|page=275-80|pmid=8050581}}</ref><ref name="ohsumi 1993">{{cite journal|title=Isolation and characterization of autophagy-defective mutants of Saccharomyces cerevisiae|journal=FEBS Letters|date=October 1993|volume=333|issue=1-2|page=169-74|pmid=8224160}}</ref><ref name="klionsky 1995">{{cite journal|title=Isolation and characterization of yeast mutants in the cytoplasm to vacuole protein targeting pathway|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1995-11_131_3/page/591|journal=Journal of Cell Biology|date=November 1995|volume=131|issue=3|page=591-602|pmid=7593182}}</ref>。其中之一人，日本科學家[[大隅良典|大隅良典]]因“對細胞自噬機制的發現”獲得2016年度的[[诺贝尔生理学或医学奖|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖]]<ref name="nobel-2016">{{cite web|url=http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2016/|title=The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 2016|publisher=Nobel Foundation|accessdate=3 October 2016|archive-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003185648/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/medicine/laureates/2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
1962年1月，美國[[洛克菲勒大學|洛克菲勒醫學研究院]]的[[基思·R·波特|基思·R·波特]]和其學生Thomas Ashford報導了添加[[胰高血糖素|胰高血糖素]]後，[[大鼠|大鼠]][[肝|肝]]細胞中的溶酶體數量增加，並且發現一些向細胞中心移位的溶酶體，包含着[[線粒體|線粒體]]等細胞器的成分。Porter和Ashford錯誤地將數據解釋為溶酶體的形成過程，不認為溶酶體是像線粒體一樣存在於[[細胞質|細胞質]]中的[[細胞器|細胞器]]，並且將觀察到的[[水解酶|水解酶]]理解為是由{{le|微體|Microbody}}產生的水解酶<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ashford TP, Porter KR | title = Cytoplasmic components in hepatic cell lysosomes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1962-01_12_1/page/198 | journal = The Journal of Cell Biology | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | pages = 198–202 | date = January 1962 | pmid = 13862833 | pmc = 2106008 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.12.1.198 }}</ref>。

1963年，赫魯班（Hruban）、Spargo及其同事等報道了局部細胞質降解的超微結構，該報道參考了1955年德國科學家的損傷誘導融合[[模型|模型]]，觀察到了從細胞質融合到生成溶酶體的三個連續步驟，並提出這個過程不僅由損傷階段誘發，而且在細胞分化的生理階段，同樣的過程也在「細胞器處置」和「細胞成分再利用」中行使功能<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Hruban Z, Spargo B, Swift H, Wissler RW, Kleinfeld RG | title = Focal cytoplasmic degradation | journal = The American Journal of Pathology | volume = 42 | issue = 6 | pages = 657–83 | date = June 1963 | pmid = 13955261 | pmc = 1949709 }}</ref>。這篇報道引起了當時也在洛克菲勒醫學研究所工作的[[克里斯汀·德·迪夫|克里斯汀·德·迪夫]]的興趣，與之前Porter和Ashford的看法不同，德迪夫受到這一發現的啟發，把這種現象命名為自噬（autophagy），並提出在胰高血糖素引發的肝細胞降解過程中，溶酶體發揮了功能。他與其[[學生|學生]]拉塞爾·德特（Russell Deter）一起證實胰高血糖素誘發的自噬是由溶酶體介導的<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Deter RL, Baudhuin P, De Duve C | title = Participation of lysosomes in cellular autophagy induced in rat liver by glucagon | journal = The Journal of Cell Biology | volume = 35 | issue = 2 | pages = C11–6 | date = November 1967 | pmid = 6055998 | pmc = 2107130 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.35.2.c11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Deter RL, De Duve C | title = Influence of glucagon, an inducer of cellular autophagy, on some physical properties of rat liver lysosomes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1967-05_33_2/page/437 | journal = The Journal of Cell Biology | volume = 33 | issue = 2 | pages = 437–49 | date = May 1967 | pmid = 4292315 | pmc = 2108350 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.33.2.437 }}</ref>，並且在1967年連續發表兩篇文章，他也由此成為第一位報道溶酶體參與細胞內自噬的[[科學家|科學家]]。這是首次確定溶酶體是細胞內自噬的部位<ref name="klionsky" /><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = de Duve C | title = Lysosomes revisited | journal = European Journal of Biochemistry | volume = 137 | issue = 3 | pages = 391–7 | date = December 1983 | pmid = 6319122 | doi = 10.1111/j.1432-1033.1983.tb07841.x }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | first1 = William A. | last1 = Dunn | first2 = Laura A. | last2 = Schroder | first3 = John P. | last3 = Aris | name-list-format = vanc | chapter = Historical overview of autophagy |editor-first = Hong-Gang | editor-last = Wang |title= Autophagy and Cancer|year= 2013 | chapter-url= https://books.google.com/books?id=nXpDAAAAQBAJ&dq |pages= 3–4 | publisher= Springer |isbn= 9781461465614}}</ref>。1974年德迪夫發現細胞內結構及功能性器官，即溶酶體和[[過氧物酶體|過氧物酶體]]，而與另外兩位科學家共享了該年度的[[諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎|諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎]]。

[[File:Yoshinori_Osumi_20161003.jpg|thumb]]
在1990年代，幾組科學家使用發芽[[酵母|酵母]]獨立地發現了自噬相關[[基因|基因]]。值得注意的是，大隅良典（他於2016年獲得了諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎，儘管有人指出該獎項可能更具包容性<ref name="nature news">{{cite journal | vauthors = Van Noorden R, Ledford H | title = Medicine Nobel for research on how cells 'eat themselves' | journal = Nature | volume = 538 | issue = 7623 | pages = 18–19 | date = October 2016 | pmid = 27708326 | doi = 10.1038/nature.2016.20721 | bibcode = 2016Natur.538...18V }}</ref>）和Michael Thumm研究了[[飢餓|飢餓]]誘導的非選擇性自噬<ref name="ohsumi 1992" /><ref name="thumm 1994" /><ref name="ohsumi 1993" />。同時，Daniel J Klionsky發現{{le|細胞質至液泡傳遞途徑|Cytoplasm-to-vacuole targeting}}（CVT），這是選擇性自噬的一種形式<ref name="klionsky 1992" /><ref name="klionsky 1995"/>。他們很快發現他們實際上是從不同的角度看本質上相同的路徑<ref name="klionksy 1996 jbc">{{cite journal | vauthors = Harding TM, Hefner-Gravink A, Thumm M, Klionsky DJ | title = Genetic and phenotypic overlap between autophagy and the cytoplasm to vacuole protein targeting pathway | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 271 | issue = 30 | pages = 17621–4 | date = July 1996 | pmid = 8663607 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.271.30.17621 }}</ref><ref name="klionsky 1996 pnas">{{cite journal | vauthors = Scott SV, Hefner-Gravink A, Morano KA, Noda T, Ohsumi Y, Klionsky DJ | title = Cytoplasm-to-vacuole targeting and autophagy employ the same machinery to deliver proteins to the yeast vacuole | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 93 | issue = 22 | pages = 12304–8 | date = October 1996 | pmid = 8901576 | pmc = 37986 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.93.22.12304 | bibcode = 1996PNAS...9312304S }}</ref>。最初，由酵母菌組發現的基因被賦予不同的名稱（APG、AUT、CVT、GSA、PAG、PAZ和PDD）。2003年，有[[研究員|研究人員]]提出了統一的命名法，即使用ATG表示自噬基因<ref name="klionsky 2003 dc">{{cite journal | vauthors = Klionsky DJ, Cregg JM, Dunn WA, Emr SD, Sakai Y, Sandoval IV, Sibirny A, Subramani S, Thumm M, Veenhuis M, Ohsumi Y | title = A unified nomenclature for yeast autophagy-related genes | journal = Developmental Cell | volume = 5 | issue = 4 | pages = 539–45 | date = October 2003 | pmid = 14536056 | doi = 10.1016/s1534-5807(03)00296-x }}</ref>。

21世紀初，自噬研究領域經歷快速的發展。ATG基因的知識為科學家提供了更方便的工具，以分析自噬在人類健康和疾病中的功能。1999年，貝絲·萊文（Beth Levine）的小組發表了一項具有里程碑意義的發現<ref name="levine 1999">{{cite journal | vauthors = Liang XH, Jackson S, Seaman M, Brown K, Kempkes B, Hibshoosh H, Levine B | title = Induction of autophagy and inhibition of tumorigenesis by beclin 1 | journal = Nature | volume = 402 | issue = 6762 | pages = 672–6 | date = December 1999 | pmid = 10604474 | doi = 10.1038/45257 | bibcode = 1999Natur.402..672L }}</ref>，將自噬與[[癌症|癌症]]聯繫起來。迄今為止，癌症與自噬之間的關係仍然是自噬研究的主要主題。自噬在神經退行性變和免疫防禦中的作用也受到了廣泛的關注。2003年，第一屆戈登自噬研究會議（Gordon Research Conference on autophagy）在沃特維爾舉行<ref name="gordon 2003">{{cite web|title=Autophagy in Stress, Development & Disease, 2003, Gordon Research Conference|url=https://www.grc.org/programs.aspx?id=10449}}</ref>。2005年，Daniel J Klionsky發行了致力於該領域的科學期刊《自噬》。2007年，首屆Keystone自噬專題討論會在[[蒙特里|蒙特里]]舉行<ref name="keystone 2007">{{cite web|title=Autophagy in Health and Disease (Z3), 2007, Keystone Symposia on Molecular and Cellular Biology|url=http://www.keystonesymposia.org/index.cfm?e=web.Meeting.Program&meetingid=838}}</ref>。2008年，Carol A Mercer創建了BHMT融合蛋白（GST-BHMT），該蛋白在[[細胞系|細胞系]]中顯示飢餓誘導的位點特異性片段化，而{{le|甜菜鹼高半胱氨酸甲基轉移酶|Betaine—homocysteine S-methyltransferase}}的降解是一種可用於評估[[哺乳類動物|哺乳類動物]]細胞中自噬通量的代謝酶<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mercer |first1=CA |last2=Kaliappan |first2=A |last3=Dennis |first3=PB |title=Macroautophagy-dependent, intralysosomal cleavage of a betaine homocysteine methyltransferase fusion protein requires stable multimerization. |journal=Autophagy |date=2008-02 |volume=4 |issue=2 |pages=185-94 |doi=10.4161/auto.5275 |pmid=18059170 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18059170-macroautophagy-dependent-intralysosomal-cleavage-of-a-betaine-homocysteine-methyltransferase-fusion-protein-requires-stable-multimerization/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

巨自噬作用、{{le|微自噬作用|Microautophagy}}和{{le|伴侶分子介導自噬作用|Chaperone-mediated autophagy}}由自噬相關基因及其相關酶介導<ref name=Lee12>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lee J, Giordano S, Zhang J | title = Autophagy, mitochondria and oxidative stress: cross-talk and redox signalling | journal = The Biochemical Journal | volume = 441 | issue = 2 | pages = 523–40 | date = January 2012 | pmid = 22187934 | pmc = 3258656 | doi = 10.1042/BJ20111451 }}</ref><ref name=Yoshimori2002>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mizushima N, Ohsumi Y, Yoshimori T | title = Autophagosome formation in mammalian cells | journal = Cell Structure and Function | volume = 27 | issue = 6 | pages = 421–9 | date = December 2002 | pmid = 12576635 | doi = 10.1247/csf.27.421 }}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite journal | vauthors = Youle RJ, Narendra DP | title = Mechanisms of mitophagy | journal = Nature Reviews. Molecular Cell Biology | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | pages = 9–14 | date = January 2011 | pmid = 21179058 | pmc = 4780047 | doi = 10.1038/nrm3028 }}</ref>。巨自噬作用細分為本體自噬和選擇性自噬（bulk and selective autophagy）。在選擇性自噬中，又細分為{{le|線粒體自噬作用|Mitophagy}}<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ding WX, Yin XM | title = Mitophagy: mechanisms, pathophysiological roles, and analysis | journal = Biological Chemistry | volume = 393 | issue = 7 | pages = 547–64 | date = July 2012 | pmid = 22944659 | pmc = 3630798 | doi = 10.1515/hsz-2012-0119 }}</ref>、脂自噬作用、[[過氧化物酶體|過氧化物酶體]]自噬作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Till A, Lakhani R, Burnett SF, Subramani S | title = Pexophagy: the selective degradation of peroxisomes | journal = International Journal of Cell Biology | volume = 2012 | pages = 512721 | date = 2012 | pmid = 22536249 | pmc = 3320016 | doi = 10.1155/2012/512721 }}</ref>、[[葉綠體|葉綠體]]自噬作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lei L | title = Chlorophagy: Preventing sunburn | journal = Nature Plants | volume = 3 | issue = 3 | pages = 17026 | date = March 2017 | pmid = 28248315 | doi = 10.1038/nplants.2017.26 }}</ref>及[[核糖體|核糖體]]自噬作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = An H, Harper JW | title = Systematic analysis of ribophagy in human cells reveals bystander flux during selective autophagy | journal = Nature Cell Biology | volume = 20 | issue = 2 | pages = 135–143 | date = February 2018 | pmid = 29230017 | pmc = 5786475 | doi = 10.1038/s41556-017-0007-x }}</ref>等。

[[File:2011_Autophagy.tif|thumb]]
*'''巨自噬作用'''是主要的自噬途徑，主要用於清除受損的細胞器或未被使用的蛋白質<ref name=Levine11>{{cite journal | vauthors = Levine B, Mizushima N, Virgin HW | title = Autophagy in immunity and inflammation | journal = Nature | volume = 469 | issue = 7330 | pages = 323–35 | date = January 2011 | pmid = 21248839 | pmc = 3131688 | doi = 10.1038/nature09782 | bibcode = 2011Natur.469..323L }}</ref>。首先，吞噬細胞將需要降解的物質吞噬，並在受損的[[細胞器|細胞器]]周圍形成[[自噬體|自噬體]]<ref name=Pegan12>{{cite journal |last1=Česen |first1=MH |last2=Pegan |first2=K |last3=Spes |first3=A |last4=Turk |first4=B |title=Lysosomal pathways to cell death and their therapeutic applications. |journal=Experimental cell research |date=2012-07-01 |volume=318 |issue=11 |pages=1245-51 |doi=10.1016/j.yexcr.2012.03.005 |pmid=22465226 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22465226/ |accessdate=2020-03-27}}</ref>。然後自噬體穿過細胞的細胞質到達溶酶體，兩個細胞器融合。在溶酶體內，自噬體內的內容物通過[[酸性|酸性]]溶酶體水解酶降解<ref name=Homma2011>{{Cite journal |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801130843/http://tp-apg.genes.nig.ac.jp/autophagy/list/GeneList.html|archive-date=2012-08-01| url = http://tp-apg.genes.nig.ac.jp/autophagy/list/GeneList.html | year = 2011 | author = Homma, K.S. | title = List of autophagy-related proteins and 3D structures | journal = Autophagy Database | volume = 290 | access-date = 2012-10-08 }}</ref> 。

[[File:Macro-micro-autophagy.gif|thumb]]
*'''微自噬作用'''涉及將細胞質內的[[物質|物質]]直接吞噬到溶酶體中<ref>{{Cite journal | title = The Discovery of Lysosomes and Autophagy | journal = Nature Education | page = 49 | volume = 3 | year = 2010 | last = Castro-Obregon|first = Susana|issue =9|url = https://www.nature.com/scitable/topicpage/the-discovery-of-lysosomes-and-autophagy-14199828}}</ref>。這是通過內陷發生的，意味著溶酶體膜向內折疊或細胞向外突出<ref name=Pegan12/>。

*'''伴侶分子介導自噬作用'''（CMA）是一個非常複雜和特異的途徑，涉及到包含hsc70的複合物的識別<ref name=Pegan12/><ref name=Cuervo2008>{{cite journal | vauthors = Bandyopadhyay U, Kaushik S, Varticovski L, Cuervo AM | title = The chaperone-mediated autophagy receptor organizes in dynamic protein complexes at the lysosomal membrane | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_2008-09_28_18/page/5747 | journal = Molecular and Cellular Biology | volume = 28 | issue = 18 | pages = 5747–63 | date = September 2008 | pmid = 18644871 | pmc = 2546938 | doi = 10.1128/MCB.02070-07 }}</ref>。這意味著蛋白質必須包含hsc70複合物的識別位點，這將使其能夠與該分子伴侶結合，形成CMA-底物/分子伴侶複合物。然後，該複合物移動到溶酶體膜結合蛋白上，該蛋白將識別並與CMA受體結合。底物蛋白在識別後就解折疊，並在溶酶體hsc70分子伴侶的幫助下，跨越溶酶體膜轉運。CMA與其他類型的自噬存在顯著差異，因為它以一種一種的方式轉運蛋白物質，並且對哪種物質穿過溶酶體屏障具有極高的選擇性<ref name=Levine11/>。

*'''線粒體自噬作用'''是通過自噬選擇性地降解受損或未受損的[[線粒體|線粒體]]。經歷損傷或受壓後，經常發生線粒體缺陷。線粒體吞噬作用促進線粒體的更新，並且防止功能異常的線粒體積聚，從而導致細胞變性。它是由酵母中的Atg3、NIX及其調節物BNIP3在哺乳動物中介導的。線粒體吞噬作用受到PINK1和parkin蛋白的調節<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gegg |first1=ME |last2=Cooper |first2=JM |last3=Chau |first3=KY |last4=Rojo |first4=M |last5=Schapira |first5=AH |last6=Taanman |first6=JW |title=Mitofusin 1 and mitofusin 2 are ubiquitinated in a PINK1/parkin-dependent manner upon induction of mitophagy. |journal=Human molecular genetics |date=2010-12-15 |volume=19 |issue=24 |pages=4861-70 |doi=10.1093/hmg/ddq419 |pmid=20871098 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20871098-mitofusin-1-and-mitofusin-2-are-ubiquitinated-in-a-pink1parkin-dependent-manner-upon-induction-of-mitophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Geisler |first1=S |last2=Holmström |first2=KM |last3=Skujat |first3=D |last4=Fiesel |first4=FC |last5=Rothfuss |first5=OC |last6=Kahle |first6=PJ |last7=Springer |first7=W |title=PINK1/Parkin-mediated mitophagy is dependent on VDAC1 and p62/SQSTM1. |journal=Nature cell biology |date=2010-02 |volume=12 |issue=2 |pages=119-31 |doi=10.1038/ncb2012 |pmid=20098416 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20098416-pink1parkin-mediated-mitophagy-is-dependent-on-vdac1-and-p62sqstm1/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

*'''脂自噬作用'''是通過自噬降解[[脂質|脂質]]<ref name=":1">{{cite journal | vauthors = Liu K, Czaja MJ | title = Regulation of lipid stores and metabolism by lipophagy | journal = Cell Death and Differentiation | volume = 20 | issue = 1 | pages = 3–11 | date = January 2013 | pmid = 22595754 | doi = 10.1038/cdd.2012.63 | pmc = 3524634 }}</ref>，該功能在[[動物|動物]]和[[真菌|真菌]]細胞中都存在<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ward C, Martinez-Lopez N, Otten EG, Carroll B, Maetzel D, Singh R, Sarkar S, Korolchuk VI | title = Autophagy, lipophagy and lysosomal lipid storage disorders | journal = Biochimica et Biophysica Acta | volume = 1861 | issue = 4 | pages = 269–84 | date = April 2016 | pmid = 26778751 | doi = 10.1016/j.bbalip.2016.01.006 }}</ref>。然而，脂肪吞噬作用在植物細胞中的作用仍然難以捉摸<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Elander PH, Minina EA, Bozhkov PV | title = Autophagy in turnover of lipid stores: trans-kingdom comparison | journal = Journal of Experimental Botany | volume = 69 | issue = 6 | pages = 1301–1311 | date = March 2018 | pmid = 29309625 | doi = 10.1093/jxb/erx433 }}</ref>。在脂質吞噬中，靶標是稱為脂質滴（LDs）的脂質結構，具有主要是三酰基甘油（TAGs）核心，以及單層磷脂和膜蛋白組成的球形細胞器。在動物細胞中，主要的脂肪吞噬途徑是通過吞噬細胞吞噬LD，即巨自噬。另一方面，在真菌細胞中，微脂代謝是主要途徑，尤其是在發芽酵母及釀酒酵母中得到了很好的研究<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = van Zutphen T, Todde V, de Boer R, Kreim M, Hofbauer HF, Wolinski H, Veenhuis M, van der Klei IJ, Kohlwein SD | title = Lipid droplet autophagy in the yeast Saccharomyces cerevisiae | journal = Molecular Biology of the Cell | volume = 25 | issue = 2 | pages = 290–301 | date = January 2014 | pmid = 24258026 | pmc = 3890349 | doi = 10.1091/mbc.E13-08-0448 }}</ref>。脂吞噬作用最早在小鼠中發現，並且在2009年發表<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Singh R, Kaushik S, Wang Y, Xiang Y, Novak I, Komatsu M, Tanaka K, Cuervo AM, Czaja MJ | title = Autophagy regulates lipid metabolism | journal = Nature | volume = 458 | issue = 7242 | pages = 1131–5 | date = April 2009 | pmid = 19339967 | pmc = 2676208 | doi = 10.1038/nature07976 | bibcode = 2009Natur.458.1131S }}</ref>。

==分子生物學==
屬於[[絲氨酸|絲氨酸]]/[[蘇氨酸|蘇氨酸]]類[[蛋白激酶|蛋白激酶]]的ATG1/ULK1是啟動自噬作用的關鍵蛋白激酶<ref name=Hosokawa/>。自噬的初始階段主要是誘導自噬和形成自噬膜，然而自噬膜的形成需要自噬前體（即自噬調控的重要節點）的形成。Beclin1-Vps34復合體是哺乳動物自噬的核心復合物。AtG4參與自噬泡的形成<ref name=Itakura/>，而UVRAG作用於自噬泡成熟及其運輸過程<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Liang |first1=C |last2=Lee |first2=JS |last3=Inn |first3=KS |last4=Gack |first4=MU |last5=Li |first5=Q |last6=Roberts |first6=EA |last7=Vergne |first7=I |last8=Deretic |first8=V |last9=Feng |first9=P |last10=Akazawa |first10=C |last11=Jung |first11=JU |title=Beclin1-binding UVRAG targets the class C Vps complex to coordinate autophagosome maturation and endocytic trafficking. |journal=Nature cell biology |date=2008-07 |volume=10 |issue=7 |pages=776-87 |doi=10.1038/ncb1740 |pmid=18552835 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18552835-beclin1-binding-uvrag-targets-the-class-c-vps-complex-to-coordinate-autophagosome-maturation-and-endocytic-trafficking/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>，Rubicon負調節其功能<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Matsunaga |first1=K |last2=Saitoh |first2=T |last3=Tabata |first3=K |last4=Omori |first4=H |last5=Satoh |first5=T |last6=Kurotori |first6=N |last7=Maejima |first7=I |last8=Shirahama-Noda |first8=K |last9=Ichimura |first9=T |last10=Isobe |first10=T |last11=Akira |first11=S |last12=Noda |first12=T |last13=Yoshimori |first13=T |title=Two Beclin 1-binding proteins, Atg14L and Rubicon, reciprocally regulate autophagy at different stages. |journal=Nature cell biology |date=2009-04 |volume=11 |issue=4 |pages=385-96 |doi=10.1038/ncb1846 |pmid=19270696 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19270696-two-beclin-1-binding-proteins-atg14l-and-rubicon-reciprocally-regulate-autophagy-at-different-stages/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。誘導自噬後，在Atg14-Vps15-mVps34復合物作用下，啟動膜泡的成核反應，進一步結合Atg21和Atg24，形成前自噬體<ref>{{cite journal |last1=He |first1=C |last2=Klionsky |first2=DJ |title=Regulation mechanisms and signaling pathways of autophagy. |journal=Annual review of genetics |date=2009 |volume=43 |pages=67-93 |doi=10.1146/annurev-genet-102808-114910 |pmid=19653858 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19653858-regulation-mechanisms-and-signaling-pathways-of-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

自噬膜泡進一步擴張並包繞底物，最終形成[[自噬體|自噬體]]。Atg12-Atg5復合物系統和LC3-Ⅱ-[[磷脂酰乙醇胺|磷脂酰乙醇胺]]復合物系統均是[[泛素|泛素]]化系統，參與着自噬體的形成。目前已知{{le|p62|Nucleoporin 62}}蛋白會誘導鑲嵌有LC3的自噬體到溶酶體，將其吞噬並清除，與底物結合的p62也能被蛋白水解酶[[生物降解|降解]]，而細胞內的[[微管|微管]]骨架其實也會將自噬體運輸到溶酶體，[[水解酶|水解酶]]在二者融合降解自噬體內容物，Rab7及{{le|UVRAG|UVRAG}}等因子參與此過程。目前已知Rab7與膜泡表面的脂分子尾部作用進行定位，而UVRAG則活化Rab7，將囊泡運送到靶位點<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Luo |first1=P |last2=Gao |first2=F |last3=Han |first3=J |last4=Sun |first4=W |last5=Li |first5=Z |title=The role of autophagy in steroid necrosis of the femoral head: a comprehensive research review. |journal=International orthopaedics |date=2018-07 |volume=42 |issue=7 |pages=1747-1753 |doi=10.1007/s00264-018-3994-8 |pmid=29797168 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29797168-the-role-of-autophagy-in-steroid-necrosis-of-the-femoral-head-a-comprehensive-research-review/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

自噬過程通常涉及兩種泛素樣[[偶聯反應|偶聯反應]]，以維持吞噬體的擴展。第1種反應發生在LC3 (酵母Atg8在哺乳動物中的同源物)，LC3對溶酶體的形成是必需的。Atg4切割LC3獲得彌散胞質狀態的LC3-Ⅰ，LC3-Ⅰ其後與磷脂酰乙醇胺偶聯，以形成膜結合狀態的LC3-Ⅱ，LC3-Ⅱ其後定位於自噬體膜。Atg5-Atg12-Atg16L1復合物與前自噬體膜相關聯，通過協助招募LC3延長它們的伸長。隨著[[吞噬細胞|吞噬細胞]]擴大並接近閉合，Atg5-Atg12-Atg16L1復合物從外膜解離，而LC3-Ⅱ仍然與完成的自噬體結合。除此之外，mAtg9是核心Atg蛋白中唯一確定的多次[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜蛋白]]，吞噬細胞的延伸也由mAtg9輔助。第2種反應則是在{{le|Atg12|ATG12}}與Atg5[[共軛|共軛]]後，Atg16L1與偶聯物Atg12-Atg5結合，形成一個對吞噬細胞成熟至關重要的Atg5-Atg12-Atg16L1復合物<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rubinsztein |first1=DC |last2=Shpilka |first2=T |last3=Elazar |first3=Z |title=Mechanisms of autophagosome biogenesis. |journal=Current biology : CB |date=2012-01-10 |volume=22 |issue=1 |pages=R29-34 |doi=10.1016/j.cub.2011.11.034 |pmid=22240478 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22240478-mechanisms-of-autophagosome-biogenesis/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

*ATG8[[酯化反應|酯化]]在自噬發生過程中的作用仍未解釋清楚，可以對促進自噬體膜的延伸和閉合起著關鍵作用。ATG8的酯化過程依賴於兩個類泛素化系統的幫助。所有[[生物|生物]]中的ATG5-ATG12共價結合復合物對於細胞內ATG8的酯化均是必須的。

*在自噬相關基因中，Beclin1、Atg5、Atg12和LC3對自噬的誘導階段十分重要。其中，LC3是自噬的關鍵蛋白，LC3前體正常會被ATG4切掉C端120個氨基酸，而殘片稱為LC3Ⅰ。胞膜形式的LC3Ⅰ在自噬發生時，已活化的LC3-Ⅰ經Atg3泛素化修飾後，與自噬泡膜表面的磷脂酰乙醇胺結合，形成自噬體膜形式且疏水性較強的LC3Ⅱ，並且[[鉚釘|鉚釘]]於自噬泡雙層膜結構上，參與細胞自噬。

*ULK復合物對自噬誘導起始至關重要<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Matsuura |first1=A |last2=Tsukada |first2=M |last3=Wada |first3=Y |last4=Ohsumi |first4=Y |title=Apg1p, a novel protein kinase required for the autophagic process in Saccharomyces cerevisiae. |journal=Gene |date=1997-06-19 |volume=192 |issue=2 |pages=245-50 |doi=10.1016/s0378-1119(97)00084-x |pmid=9224897 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9224897-apg1p-a-novel-protein-kinase-required-for-the-autophagic-process-in-saccharomyces-cerevisiae/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>，主要由ULK1/2、自噬相關基因13（ATG13）、ATG101和200 kD家族相互作用蛋白組成<ref name=Hosokawa>{{cite journal |last1=Hosokawa |first1=N |last2=Hara |first2=T |last3=Kaizuka |first3=T |last4=Kishi |first4=C |last5=Takamura |first5=A |last6=Miura |first6=Y |last7=Iemura |first7=S |last8=Natsume |first8=T |last9=Takehana |first9=K |last10=Yamada |first10=N |last11=Guan |first11=JL |last12=Oshiro |first12=N |last13=Mizushima |first13=N |title=Nutrient-dependent mTORC1 association with the ULK1-Atg13-FIP200 complex required for autophagy. |journal=Molecular biology of the cell |date=2009-04 |volume=20 |issue=7 |pages=1981-91 |doi=10.1091/mbc.e08-12-1248 |pmid=19211835 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19211835-nutrient-dependent-mtorc1-association-with-the-ulk1-atg13-fip200-complex-required-for-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。ULK1/2負責募集ATG蛋白，其中ULK1是哺乳動物自噬泡形成所必需的一種[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]，其活性缺失時LC3-Ⅱ不能形成，阻礙自噬過程。ULK1激酶復合體能夠促進PI3K和ATG14形成復合物，並且促進Beclin1從Bcl2-Beclin1復合體中解離出來，形成參與自噬體核形成的關鍵因子Beclin1-PI3K-ATG14復合物<ref name=Itakura>{{cite journal |last1=Itakura |first1=E |last2=Kishi |first2=C |last3=Inoue |first3=K |last4=Mizushima |first4=N |title=Beclin 1 forms two distinct phosphatidylinositol 3-kinase complexes with mammalian Atg14 and UVRAG. |journal=Molecular biology of the cell |date=2008-12 |volume=19 |issue=12 |pages=5360-72 |doi=10.1091/mbc.e08-01-0080 |pmid=18843052 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18843052-beclin-1-forms-two-distinct-phosphatidylinositol-3-kinase-complexes-with-mammalian-atg14-and-uvrag/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。{{le|單磷酸腺苷活化蛋白質激酶|AMP-activated protein kinase}}（AMPK）和mTOR都可以催化ULK1的磷酸化<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Chan EY | title = Regulation and function of uncoordinated-51 like kinase proteins | journal = Antioxidants & Redox Signaling | volume = 17 | issue = 5 | pages = 775–85 | date = September 2012 | pmid = 22074133 | doi = 10.1089/ars.2011.4396 }}</ref> 。AMPK在營養充足的條件下失活，mTORC活化並磷酸化ULK1和ATG13，從而抑制自噬起始。AMPK在飢餓條件下活化，同時mTORC失活，已活化的AMPK[[催化|催化]]ULK1絲氨酸磷酸化，促進自噬作用。除此之外，ATG13可以由{{le|mTORC1|mTORC1}}磷酸化並調控ULK復合物的活性，ATG101結合並穩定FIP200，而FIP200則為ULK及ATG13提供支架<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Choi |first1=Y |last2=Bowman |first2=JW |last3=Jung |first3=JU |title=Autophagy during viral infection - a double-edged sword. |journal=Nature reviews. Microbiology |date=2018-06 |volume=16 |issue=6 |pages=341-354 |doi=10.1038/s41579-018-0003-6 |pmid=29556036 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29556036-autophagy-during-viral-infection-a-double-edged-sword/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

*PI3K復合物由Vps34、Vps15、Beclin1和Atg14蛋白組成，ULK1復合物在膜泡形成後會從由[[細胞質|細胞質]]轉移至[[內質網|內質網]]，並且增強PI3K復合物的活性，隨後可產生磷脂酰肌醇-3磷酸酯，促進其他效應蛋白與自噬體膜結合，從而啟動膜泡的成核反應，繼而介導前自噬體的形成<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ohsumi |first1=Y |title=Historical landmarks of autophagy research. |journal=Cell research |date=2014-01 |volume=24 |issue=1 |pages=9-23 |doi=10.1038/cr.2013.169 |pmid=24366340 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24366340-historical-landmarks-of-autophagy-research/ |accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>。

==功能==
===營養不足===
自噬在各種細胞功能中都發揮作用。[[營養不良|營養不足]]會導致高水平的自噬，降解不需要的蛋白質，並且回收氨基酸，以合成對細胞生存至關重要的蛋白質<ref name=Klionsky2002>{{cite journal | vauthors = Reggiori F, Klionsky DJ | title = Autophagy in the eukaryotic cell | journal = Eukaryotic Cell | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | pages = 11–21 | date = February 2002 | pmid = 12455967 | pmc = 118053 | doi = 10.1128/EC.01.1.11-21.2002 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Klionsky DJ, Emr SD | title = Autophagy as a regulated pathway of cellular degradation | journal = Science | volume = 290 | issue = 5497 | pages = 1717–21 | date = December 2000 | pmid = 11099404 | doi = 10.1126/science.290.5497.1717 | pmc = 2732363 | bibcode = 2000Sci...290.1717K }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Levine B, Klionsky DJ | title = Development by self-digestion: molecular mechanisms and biological functions of autophagy | journal = Developmental Cell | volume = 6 | issue = 4 | pages = 463–77 | date = April 2004 | pmid = 15068787 | doi = 10.1016/S1534-5807(04)00099-1 }}</ref>。在高等真核生物中，自噬作用因動物在出生後切斷了來自[[胎盤|胎盤]]的食物供應而被響應<ref name=Kuma2004>{{cite journal | vauthors = Kuma A, Hatano M, Matsui M, Yamamoto A, Nakaya H, Yoshimori T, Ohsumi Y, Tokuhisa T, Mizushima N | title = The role of autophagy during the early neonatal starvation period | journal = Nature | volume = 432 | issue = 7020 | pages = 1032–6 | date = December 2004 | pmid = 15525940 | doi = 10.1038/nature03029 | displayauthors = etal | bibcode = 2004Natur.432.1032K }}</ref><ref name=Ohsumi2004>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mizushima N, Yamamoto A, Matsui M, Yoshimori T, Ohsumi Y | title = In vivo analysis of autophagy in response to nutrient starvation using transgenic mice expressing a fluorescent autophagosome marker | journal = Molecular Biology of the Cell | volume = 15 | issue = 3 | pages = 1101–11 | date = March 2004 | pmid = 14699058 | pmc = 363084 | doi = 10.1091/mbc.E03-09-0704 }}</ref>。自噬能力降低的突變酵母細胞會在營養缺乏的情況下迅速消失<ref name=Tsukada93>{{cite journal | vauthors = Tsukada M, Ohsumi Y | title = Isolation and characterization of autophagy-defective mutants of Saccharomyces cerevisiae | journal = FEBS Letters | volume = 333 | issue = 1–2 | pages = 169–74 | date = October 1993 | pmid = 8224160 | doi = 10.1016/0014-5793(93)80398-E }}</ref>。對APG突變體的研究表明，在飢餓條件下，通過自噬體進行的自噬對於液泡中的蛋白質降解是必不可少的，並且酵母中至少有15個APG基因參與自噬<ref name=Tsukada93/>。營養素介導的自噬涉及一種稱為ATG7的基因，因為小鼠研究表明，APG7缺陷型小鼠有着飢餓引起的自噬<ref name=Ohsumi2004/>。

===異種吞噬===
在[[微生物學|微生物學]]中，{{le|異種吞噬|Xenophagy}}是指感染性顆粒的自噬性降解。細胞自噬機制在先天免疫中發揮重要作用。結核桿菌等細胞內的病原體被靶向降解，當中的細胞機制和調控機制與靶向線粒體降解的機制相同<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Gutierrez MG, Master SS, Singh SB, Taylor GA, Colombo MI, Deretic V | title = Autophagy is a defense mechanism inhibiting BCG and Mycobacterium tuberculosis survival in infected macrophages | journal = Cell | volume = 119 | issue = 6 | pages = 753–66 | date = December 2004 | pmid = 15607973 | doi = 10.1016/j.cell.2004.11.038 }}</ref> 。這是[[共生體學說|內共生學說]]的進一步證據。儘管某些細菌會阻止吞噬體成熟為降解的細胞器，稱為{{le|吞噬溶酶體|Phagolysosome}}，但是這個過程通常會導致由侵入性[[微生物|微生物]]帶來的破壞<ref name=Deretic2009>{{cite book | vauthors = Deretic V, Delgado M, Vergne I, Master S, De Haro S, Ponpuak M, Singh S | chapter = Autophagy in immunity against mycobacterium tuberculosis: a model system to dissect immunological roles of autophagy | volume = 335 | pages = 169–88 | year = 2009 | pmid = 19802565 | pmc = 2788935 | doi = 10.1007/978-3-642-00302-8_8 | isbn = 978-3-642-00301-1 | series = Current Topics in Microbiology and Immunology | title = Autophagy in Infection and Immunity }}</ref>。

===感染===
水皰性口炎病毒是由自噬體從胞質溶膠中吸收並轉移到內體中，並且在那裡通過{{le|TLR7|TLR7}}檢測單鏈[[核糖核酸|核糖核酸]]。在[[類鐸受體|類鐸受體]]被激活後，細胞內信號級聯反應就會開始，導致干擾素和其他抗病毒[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]的誘導。部分病毒和細菌破壞了自噬途徑，以促進自身複製<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Jackson WT, Giddings TH, Taylor MP, Mulinyawe S, Rabinovitch M, Kopito RR, Kirkegaard K | title = Subversion of cellular autophagosomal machinery by RNA viruses | journal = PLoS Biology | volume = 3 | issue = 5 | pages = e156 | date = May 2005 | pmid = 15884975 | pmc = 1084330 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pbio.0030156 }} {{open access}}</ref>。半乳凝素8已經被鑑定為細胞內的「危險受體」，能夠啟動針對細胞內病原體的自噬。當半乳凝素8與受損的[[液泡|液泡]]結合時，它會募集{{le|CALCOCO2|CALCOCO2}}等自噬受體，導致自噬體的形成和細菌的降解<ref name=":3">{{cite journal | vauthors = Thurston TL, Wandel MP, von Muhlinen N, Foeglein A, Randow F | title = Galectin 8 targets damaged vesicles for autophagy to defend cells against bacterial invasion | journal = Nature | volume = 482 | issue = 7385 | pages = 414–8 | date = January 2012 | pmid = 22246324 | pmc = 3343631 | doi = 10.1038/nature10744 | bibcode = 2012Natur.482..414T }}</ref> 。 
===修復機制===
自噬可以降解受損的細胞器、[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]和[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]，而抵制自噬作用被認為是造成受損細胞蓄積和[[衰老|衰老]]的其中一個主要原因<ref name=Cuervo2005>{{cite journal | vauthors = Cuervo AM, Bergamini E, Brunk UT, Dröge W, Ffrench M, Terman A | title = Autophagy and aging: the importance of maintaining "clean" cells | journal = Autophagy | volume = 1 | issue = 3 | pages = 131–40 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16874025 | doi = 10.4161/auto.1.3.2017 }}</ref>。自噬和自噬調節劑參與溶酶體損傷的反應，通常由{{le|半乳凝素-3|Galectin-3}}和{{le|半乳凝素-8|Galectin-8}}等{{le|半乳凝素|Galectin}}指導，半乳凝素-8負責募集{{le|TRIM16|TRIM16}}。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Chauhan S, Kumar S, Jain A, Ponpuak M, Mudd MH, Kimura T, Choi SW, Peters R, Mandell M, Bruun JA, Johansen T, Deretic V | title = TRIMs and Galectins Globally Cooperate and TRIM16 and Galectin-3 Co-direct Autophagy in Endomembrane Damage Homeostasis | journal = Developmental Cell | volume = 39 | issue = 1 | pages = 13–27 | date = October 2016 | pmid = 27693506 | pmc = 5104201 | doi = 10.1016/j.devcel.2016.08.003 }}</ref>和NDP52等[[受體|受體]]，並直接影響mTOR和AMPK的活性，而mTOR和AMPK分別抑制和激活自噬作用<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Jia J, Abudu YP, Claude-Taupin A, Gu Y, Kumar S, Choi SW, Peters R, Mudd MH, Allers L, Salemi M, Phinney B, Johansen T, Deretic V | title = Galectins Control mTOR in Response to Endomembrane Damage | language = en | journal = Molecular Cell | volume = 70 | issue = 1 | pages = 120–135.e8 | date = April 2018 | pmid = 29625033 | pmc = 5911935 | doi = 10.1016/j.molcel.2018.03.009 }}</ref>

===程序性細胞死亡===
[[程序性細胞死亡|程序性細胞死亡]]（PCD）的其中一個機制與自噬小體的出現有關，並且依賴於自噬蛋白。這種細胞死亡形式最有可能與形態學上定義為自噬PCD（autophagic PCD）的過程相對應。其中一個問題，是步入死亡過程的細胞中，其自噬的活性是導致其死亡的原因，還是為了防止細胞死亡的一個嘗試。迄今為止，形態學和組織化學研究並未證明自噬過程與細胞死亡之間存在因果關係。最近有論據認為，垂死細胞中的自噬活性可能是一種生存機制<ref name=tavassoly>{{cite book|last1=Tavassoly|first1=Iman | name-list-format = vanc |title=Dynamics of Cell Fate Decision Mediated by the Interplay of Autophagy and Apoptosis in Cancer Cells|date=2015|publisher=Springer International Publishing|isbn=978-3-319-14962-2|pages=|doi=10.1007/978-3-319-14962-2 |series=Springer Theses }}</ref><ref name=Shimizu2005>{{cite journal | vauthors = Tsujimoto Y, Shimizu S | title = Another way to die: autophagic programmed cell death | journal = Cell Death and Differentiation | volume = 12 Suppl 2 | issue = Suppl 2 | pages = 1528–34 | date = November 2005 | pmid = 16247500 | doi = 10.1038/sj.cdd.4401777 }}</ref>。對昆蟲變態的研究表明，細胞經歷了一種PCD形式，這種形式與其他形式截然不同。這些已被提議作為自噬作用使細胞死亡的例子<ref name=Osborne1993>{{cite journal | vauthors = Schwartz LM, Smith SW, Jones ME, Osborne BA | title = Do all programmed cell deaths occur via apoptosis? | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 90 | issue = 3 | pages = 980–4 | date = February 1993 | pmid = 8430112 | pmc = 45794 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.90.3.980 | bibcode = 1993PNAS...90..980S }}</ref> 。最近的藥理和生化研究表明，有助細胞生存或致死的自噬可以通過應激期間，尤其是病毒[[感染|感染]]後，調控信號的類型和程度來區分<ref name=Datan>{{cite journal | vauthors = Datan E, Shirazian A, Benjamin S, Matassov D, Tinari A, Malorni W, Lockshin RA, Garcia-Sastre A, Zakeri Z | title = mTOR/p70S6K signaling distinguishes routine, maintenance-level autophagy from autophagic cell death during influenza A infection | journal = Virology | volume = 452-453 | issue = March 2014 | pages = 175–190 | date = March 2014 | pmid = 24606695 | pmc = 4005847 | doi = 10.1016/j.virol.2014.01.008 }}</ref> 。然而尚未在病毒系統之外觀察到這些發現。

==影響自噬的因素及其影響==
===力學方面===
*[[左心室|左心室]][[心肌|心肌]]組織中，壓力超負荷會導致其[[蛋白酶|蛋白酶]]的表達量和活性均顯著增強（目前已知蛋白酶的活性與自噬作用存在密切的關係）<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Depre |first1=C |last2=Wang |first2=Q |last3=Yan |first3=L |last4=Hedhli |first4=N |last5=Peter |first5=P |last6=Chen |first6=L |last7=Hong |first7=C |last8=Hittinger |first8=L |last9=Ghaleh |first9=B |last10=Sadoshima |first10=J |last11=Vatner |first11=DE |last12=Vatner |first12=SF |last13=Madura |first13=K |title=Activation of the cardiac proteasome during pressure overload promotes ventricular hypertrophy. |journal=Circulation |date=2006-10-24 |volume=114 |issue=17 |pages=1821-8 |doi=10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.106.637827 |pmid=17043166 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17043166-activation-of-the-cardiac-proteasome-during-pressure-overload-promotes-ventricular-hypertrophy/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>，並且導致小鼠心肌細胞的自噬活性持續地增強，甚至發現升高的情況維持至少3周<ref name=Zhu>{{cite journal |last1=Zhu |first1=H |last2=Tannous |first2=P |last3=Johnstone |first3=JL |last4=Kong |first4=Y |last5=Shelton |first5=JM |last6=Richardson |first6=JA |last7=Le |first7=V |last8=Levine |first8=B |last9=Rothermel |first9=BA |last10=Hill |first10=JA |title=Cardiac autophagy is a maladaptive response to hemodynamic stress. |journal=The Journal of clinical investigation |date=2007-07 |volume=117 |issue=7 |pages=1782-93 |doi=10.1172/JCI27523 |pmid=17607355 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17607355-cardiac-autophagy-is-a-maladaptive-response-to-hemodynamic-stress/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。許多研究證實心肌細胞的自噬活性因壓力超負荷而提高<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fu |first1=L |last2=Wei |first2=CC |last3=Powell |first3=PC |last4=Bradley |first4=WE |last5=Collawn |first5=JF |last6=Dell'Italia |first6=LJ |title=Volume overload induces autophagic degradation of procollagen in cardiac fibroblasts. |journal=Journal of molecular and cellular cardiology |date=2015-12 |volume=89 |issue=Pt B |pages=241-250 |doi=10.1016/j.yjmcc.2015.10.027 |pmid=26596413 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4689667/#__ffn_sectitle |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lin |first1=L |last2=Liu |first2=X |last3=Xu |first3=J |last4=Weng |first4=L |last5=Ren |first5=J |last6=Ge |first6=J |last7=Zou |first7=Y |title=High-density lipoprotein inhibits mechanical stress-induced cardiomyocyte autophagy and cardiac hypertrophy through angiotensin II type 1 receptor-mediated PI3K/Akt pathway. |journal=Journal of cellular and molecular medicine |date=2015-08 |volume=19 |issue=8 |pages=1929-38 |doi=10.1111/jcmm.12567 |pmid=25946687 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25946687-high-density-lipoprotein-inhibits-mechanical-stress-induced-cardiomyocyte-autophagy-and-cardiac-hypertrophy-through-angiotensin-ii-type-1-receptor-mediated-pi3kakt-pathway/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Weng |first1=LQ |last2=Zhang |first2=WB |last3=Ye |first3=Y |last4=Yin |first4=PP |last5=Yuan |first5=J |last6=Wang |first6=XX |last7=Kang |first7=L |last8=Jiang |first8=SS |last9=You |first9=JY |last10=Wu |first10=J |last11=Gong |first11=H |last12=Ge |first12=JB |last13=Zou |first13=YZ |title=Aliskiren ameliorates pressure overload-induced heart hypertrophy and fibrosis in mice. |journal=Acta pharmacologica Sinica |date=2014-08 |volume=35 |issue=8 |pages=1005-14 |doi=10.1038/aps.2014.45 |pmid=24998254 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24998254-aliskiren-ameliorates-pressure-overload-induced-heart-hypertrophy-and-fibrosis-in-mice/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。因為壓力超負荷使心肌細胞中，在[[細胞核|細胞核]]周圍逐漸聚集的錯誤折疊蛋白數量增多，並且形成被細胞自噬系統識別並降解的聚集體。其後的科研人員利用[[動脈|動脈]]結扎的方法，使已經敲除Beclin-1的[[雜合子|雜合子]]小鼠心臟處於壓力超負荷的狀況，最終發現敲除Beclin-1可以減弱壓力超負荷造成的細胞自噬活性提高，並且減弱心肌細胞對壓力超負荷的病理性重建作用，同時又發現在小鼠體內過度表達Beclin-1則造成相反的作用<ref name=Zhu/>。另一些科研人員進行的實驗也證明了心肌細胞為了維持細胞穩態和心肌的正常結構及功能，而擁有基礎水平的細胞自噬作用。當心肌面對着血流壓力超負荷的狀況時，自噬作用的提升就是心肌應對這種狀況的適應性反應。若然{{le|ATG5|ATG5}}等自噬相關基因被特異性敲除，小鼠[[In_vivo|體內]]會出現[[左心室|左心室]]擴張及收縮功能減弱等異常現象，甚至在2周後出現了心肌肥大的問題<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nakai |first1=A |last2=Yamaguchi |first2=O |last3=Takeda |first3=T |last4=Higuchi |first4=Y |last5=Hikoso |first5=S |last6=Taniike |first6=M |last7=Omiya |first7=S |last8=Mizote |first8=I |last9=Matsumura |first9=Y |last10=Asahi |first10=M |last11=Nishida |first11=K |last12=Hori |first12=M |last13=Mizushima |first13=N |last14=Otsu |first14=K |title=The role of autophagy in cardiomyocytes in the basal state and in response to hemodynamic stress. |journal=Nature medicine |date=2007-05 |volume=13 |issue=5 |pages=619-24 |doi=10.1038/nm1574 |pmid=17450150 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17450150-the-role-of-autophagy-in-cardiomyocytes-in-the-basal-state-and-in-response-to-hemodynamic-stress/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。除此之外，有多份研究指出壓力超負荷的情況消失時，細胞會逐漸回復正常的形態，而自噬則發揮著重要的作用。當去除小鼠[[主動脈|主動脈]]結扎後，會發現心肌細胞逐漸復原，並且觀察到自噬相關標誌分子LC3b-Ⅱ的表達提高，反映自噬作用的活性極大地提升<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hariharan |first1=N |last2=Ikeda |first2=Y |last3=Hong |first3=C |last4=Alcendor |first4=RR |last5=Usui |first5=S |last6=Gao |first6=S |last7=Maejima |first7=Y |last8=Sadoshima |first8=J |title=Autophagy plays an essential role in mediating regression of hypertrophy during unloading of the heart. |journal=PloS one |date=2013 |volume=8 |issue=1 |pages=e51632 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0051632 |pmid=23308102 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23308102-autophagy-plays-an-essential-role-in-mediating-regression-of-hypertrophy-during-unloading-of-the-heart/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

*心肌細胞若然處於去[[應力|應力]]負荷的環境，其自噬作用會受到影響，然而自噬作用能其所促進或降低。有些研究人員心肌细胞處於去應力負荷的環境時會萎缩，並且發現LC3b-Ⅱ和Beclin-1的表達提升<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Cao |first1=DJ |last2=Jiang |first2=N |last3=Blagg |first3=A |last4=Johnstone |first4=JL |last5=Gondalia |first5=R |last6=Oh |first6=M |last7=Luo |first7=X |last8=Yang |first8=KC |last9=Shelton |first9=JM |last10=Rothermel |first10=BA |last11=Gillette |first11=TG |last12=Dorn |first12=GW |last13=Hill |first13=JA |title=Mechanical unloading activates FoxO3 to trigger Bnip3-dependent cardiomyocyte atrophy. |journal=Journal of the American Heart Association |date=2013-04-08 |volume=2 |issue=2 |pages=e000016 |doi=10.1161/JAHA.113.000016 |pmid=23568341 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23568341-mechanical-unloading-activates-foxo3-to-trigger-bnip3-dependent-cardiomyocyte-atrophy/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。然而，科研人員發現有佩戴左心室輔助裝置的[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]][[患者|患者]]，體內心肌細胞自噬的水平會降低，推測可能是因為心肌細胞的能量[[需求|需求]]降低，不再需要維持高水平的自噬活性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kassiotis |first1=C |last2=Ballal |first2=K |last3=Wellnitz |first3=K |last4=Vela |first4=D |last5=Gong |first5=M |last6=Salazar |first6=R |last7=Frazier |first7=OH |last8=Taegtmeyer |first8=H |title=Markers of autophagy are downregulated in failing human heart after mechanical unloading. |journal=Circulation |date=2009-09-15 |volume=120 |issue=11 Suppl |pages=S191-7 |doi=10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.108.842252 |pmid=19752367 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19752367-markers-of-autophagy-are-downregulated-in-failing-human-heart-after-mechanical-unloading/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

*自噬在力學[[刺激|刺激]]或衝擊引起的[[軟骨|軟骨]]反應中，發揮重要的作用。最先研究有關方面的研究人員發現遭受40%力學衝擊的細胞的存活率會降低，並且發現[[細胞外基質|細胞外基質]]中[[硫酸|硫酸]]化[[糖胺聚糖|糖胺聚糖]]逐漸丟失，同時在24小時後檢測到LC3b-Ⅱ的表達提高，然而在48[[小時|小時]]後細胞的自噬逐漸受到了抑制<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Caramés |first1=B |last2=Taniguchi |first2=N |last3=Seino |first3=D |last4=Blanco |first4=FJ |last5=D'Lima |first5=D |last6=Lotz |first6=M |title=Mechanical injury suppresses autophagy regulators and pharmacologic activation of autophagy results in chondroprotection. |journal=Arthritis and rheumatism |date=2012-04 |volume=64 |issue=4 |pages=1182-92 |doi=10.1002/art.33444 |pmid=22034068 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22034068-mechanical-injury-suppresses-autophagy-regulators-and-pharmacologic-activation-of-autophagy-results-in-chondroprotection/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。由此可見，自噬作用在軟骨組織面對力學衝擊時，會有一定程度的保護作用，但是在損傷過大時，就會因受到[[抑制|抑制]]而失去對軟骨組織的保護作用。除此之外，有不少科研人員指出不同時程的力學刺激，對軟骨細胞的自噬影響存在着差異。例如短時程的間歇循環機械[[張力|張力]]可以促進軟骨細胞的自噬作用，而長時程則有相反的結果<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xu |first1=Hong-guang |last2=Yu |first2=Yun-fei |last3=Zheng |first3=Quan |last4=Zhang |first4=Wei |last5=Wang |first5=Chuang-dong |last6=Zhao |first6=Xiao-yin |last7=Tong |first7=Wen-xue |last8=Wang |first8=Hong |last9=Liu |first9=Ping |last10=Zhang |first10=Xiao-ling |title=Autophagy protects end plate chondrocytes from intermittent cyclic mechanical tension induced calcification |journal=Bone |date=2014-09 |volume=66 |pages=232–239 |doi=10.1016/j.bone.2014.06.018 |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>

*層流剪切力對[[血管|血管]][[內皮|內皮細胞]]的自噬的影響在2014年已被證實。其後的研究發現層流剪切力可以促進內皮細胞的自噬活性，可能跟細胞內氧化-抗氧化平衡有關<ref name=Bharath/>，而較小的層流剪切力及震蕩流剪切力卻不能夠促進自噬活性。流動剪切力（即適當的層流剪切力）能夠幫助維持內皮細胞的自噬作用，內皮細胞在加載流動剪切力後會維持[[相對靜止|靜止]]狀態，同時自噬的活性逐漸降低到基礎水平<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Guo |first1=F |last2=Li |first2=X |last3=Peng |first3=J |last4=Tang |first4=Y |last5=Yang |first5=Q |last6=Liu |first6=L |last7=Wang |first7=Z |last8=Jiang |first8=Z |last9=Xiao |first9=M |last10=Ni |first10=C |last11=Chen |first11=R |last12=Wei |first12=D |last13=Wang |first13=GX |title=Autophagy regulates vascular endothelial cell eNOS and ET-1 expression induced by laminar shear stress in an ex vivo perfused system. |journal=Annals of biomedical engineering |date=2014-09 |volume=42 |issue=9 |pages=1978-88 |doi=10.1007/s10439-014-1033-5 |pmid=24838486 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24838486-autophagy-regulates-vascular-endothelial-cell-enos-and-et-1-expression-induced-by-laminar-shear-stress-in-an-ex-vivo-perfused-system/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。除此之外，有科研人員指出流動剪切力在炎症狀態下，對內皮細胞自噬的促進作用也會增強<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ding |first1=Z |last2=Liu |first2=S |last3=Deng |first3=X |last4=Fan |first4=Y |last5=Wang |first5=X |last6=Mehta |first6=JL |title=Hemodynamic shear stress modulates endothelial cell autophagy: Role of LOX-1. |journal=International journal of cardiology |date=2015-04-01 |volume=184 |pages=86-95 |doi=10.1016/j.ijcard.2015.01.065 |pmid=25697875 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25697875-hemodynamic-shear-stress-modulates-endothelial-cell-autophagy-role-of-lox-1/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>，並且起到抗炎症反應的作用<ref name=Bharath>{{cite journal |last1=Bharath |first1=LP |last2=Mueller |first2=R |last3=Li |first3=Y |last4=Ruan |first4=T |last5=Kunz |first5=D |last6=Goodrich |first6=R |last7=Mills |first7=T |last8=Deeter |first8=L |last9=Sargsyan |first9=A |last10=Anandh Babu |first10=PV |last11=Graham |first11=TE |last12=Symons |first12=JD |title=Impairment of autophagy in endothelial cells prevents shear-stress-induced increases in nitric oxide bioavailability. |journal=Canadian journal of physiology and pharmacology |date=2014-07 |volume=92 |issue=7 |pages=605-12 |doi=10.1139/cjpp-2014-0017 |pmid=24941409 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24941409-impairment-of-autophagy-in-endothelial-cells-prevents-shear-stress-induced-increases-in-nitric-oxide-bioavailability/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

*在受到機械損傷及壓縮損傷時<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chen |first1=Z |last2=Fu |first2=Q |last3=Shen |first3=B |last4=Huang |first4=X |last5=Wang |first5=K |last6=He |first6=P |last7=Li |first7=F |last8=Zhang |first8=F |last9=Shen |first9=H |title=Enhanced p62 expression triggers concomitant autophagy and apoptosis in a rat chronic spinal cord compression model. |journal=Molecular medicine reports |date=2014-06 |volume=9 |issue=6 |pages=2091-6 |doi=10.3892/mmr.2014.2124 |pmid=24715058 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24715058-enhanced-p62-expression-triggers-concomitant-autophagy-and-apoptosis-in-a-rat-chronic-spinal-cord-compression-model/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>，神經細胞會提升自噬的水平<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chen |first1=HC |last2=Fong |first2=TH |last3=Hsu |first3=PW |last4=Chiu |first4=WT |title=Multifaceted effects of rapamycin on functional recovery after spinal cord injury in rats through autophagy promotion, anti-inflammation, and neuroprotection. |journal=The Journal of surgical research |date=2013-01 |volume=179 |issue=1 |pages=e203-10 |doi=10.1016/j.jss.2012.02.023 |pmid=22482761 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22482761-multifaceted-effects-of-rapamycin-on-functional-recovery-after-spinal-cord-injury-in-rats-through-autophagy-promotion-anti-inflammation-and-neuroprotection/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>，在細胞受損早期可以透過抑制[[細胞凋亡|細胞凋亡]]的途徑來保護神經細胞。除此之外，[[力學|力學]]因素對[[肝癌|肝癌]]細胞<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lien |first1=SC |last2=Chang |first2=SF |last3=Lee |first3=PL |last4=Wei |first4=SY |last5=Chang |first5=MD |last6=Chang |first6=JY |last7=Chiu |first7=JJ |title=Mechanical regulation of cancer cell apoptosis and autophagy: roles of bone morphogenetic protein receptor, Smad1/5, and p38 MAPK. |journal=Biochimica et biophysica acta |date=2013-12 |volume=1833 |issue=12 |pages=3124-3133 |doi=10.1016/j.bbamcr.2013.08.023 |pmid=24021264 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24021264-mechanical-regulation-of-cancer-cell-apoptosis-and-autophagy-roles-of-bone-morphogenetic-protein-receptor-smad15-and-p38-mapk/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>、{{le|精原瘤|Seminoma}}細胞、[[成纖維細胞|成纖維細胞]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chen |first1=H |last2=Chen |first2=L |last3=Cheng |first3=B |last4=Jiang |first4=C |title=Cyclic mechanical stretching induces autophagic cell death in tenofibroblasts through activation of prostaglandin E2 production. |journal=Cellular physiology and biochemistry : international journal of experimental cellular physiology, biochemistry, and pharmacology |date=2015 |volume=36 |issue=1 |pages=24-33 |doi=10.1159/000374050 |pmid=25924624 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25924624-cyclic-mechanical-stretching-induces-autophagic-cell-death-in-tenofibroblasts-through-activation-of-prostaglandin-e2-production/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>、[[足細胞|足細胞]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Li |first1=D |last2=Lu |first2=Z |last3=Xu |first3=Z |last4=Ji |first4=J |last5=Zheng |first5=Z |last6=Lin |first6=S |last7=Yan |first7=T |title=Spironolactone promotes autophagy via inhibiting PI3K/AKT/mTOR signalling pathway and reduce adhesive capacity damage in podocytes under mechanical stress. |journal=Bioscience reports |date=2016-08 |volume=36 |issue=4 |doi=10.1042/BSR20160086 |pmid=27129295 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4937173/#__ffn_sectitle |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>及小梁細胞等細胞自噬的促進作用也被一些研究人員所報道<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Porter |first1=KM |last2=Jeyabalan |first2=N |last3=Liton |first3=PB |title=MTOR-independent induction of autophagy in trabecular meshwork cells subjected to biaxial stretch. |journal=Biochimica et biophysica acta |date=2014-06 |volume=1843 |issue=6 |pages=1054-62 |doi=10.1016/j.bbamcr.2014.02.010 |pmid=24583119 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24583119-mtor-independent-induction-of-autophagy-in-trabecular-meshwork-cells-subjected-to-biaxial-stretch/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

===氨基酸===
*當胞內[[賴氨酸|賴氨酸]]（Lys）不足時，[[骨骼肌|骨骼肌]]細胞會因自噬-溶酶體途徑被激活而發生自噬，使得自身的蛋白質被降解，以抵抗外部因素引起的氨基酸缺乏，在短時間內維持自身氨基酸的[[平衡|平衡]]狀態<ref name=Sato>{{cite journal |last1=Sato |first1=T |last2=Ito |first2=Y |last3=Nagasawa |first3=T |title=Regulation of skeletal muscle protein degradation and synthesis by oral administration of lysine in rats. |journal=Journal of nutritional science and vitaminology |date=2013 |volume=59 |issue=5 |pages=412-9 |doi=10.3177/jnsv.59.412 |pmid=24418875 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24418875-regulation-of-skeletal-muscle-protein-degradation-and-synthesis-by-oral-administration-of-lysine-in-rats/ |accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref>。

*[[白胺酸|白胺酸]]（Leu）是必需的[[支鏈氨基酸|支鏈氨基酸]]，然而因Leu不能在動物體內合成而只可以從[[食物|食物]]中攝取。目前已經有多項研究將Leu剝奪而引起的蛋白質分解與自噬聯繫着， 有研究表明miR-20a和miR-106b（均為miR-17 microRNA家族）可能通過抑制小鼠成肌細胞系[[C2C12|C2C12]]中{{le|Unc-51樣自噬激活激酶1|ULK1}}的表達，調節因Leu被剝奪而誘導的自噬<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wu |first1=Hao |last2=Wang |first2=Fengli |last3=Hu |first3=Shenglan |last4=Yin |first4=Cong |last5=Li |first5=Xiao |last6=Zhao |first6=Shuhong |last7=Wang |first7=Junjun |last8=Yan |first8=Xianghua |title=MiR-20a and miR-106b negatively regulate autophagy induced by leucine deprivation via suppression of ULK1 expression in C2C12 myoblasts |journal=Cellular Signalling |date=2012-11 |volume=24 |issue=11 |pages=2179–2186 |doi=10.1016/j.cellsig.2012.07.001 |accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref>。另外一份研究則發現，自噬-溶酶體系統會攝入Leu後被激活，抑制肌原纖維蛋白質的降解，接着發現，在C2C12細胞（經[[達爾伯克氏必需基本培養基|達爾伯克氏必需基本培養基]]培養）中，補充Leu 30[[分鐘|分鐘]]之後，LC3-Ⅱ與LC3-Ⅰ的比值顯著降低，顯示補充Leu會顯著抑制C2C12細胞自噬的發生<ref name=Sato/>。由於缺乏氨基酸可以誘導細胞發生自噬，所以Leu是一種有效的自噬抑制劑<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rautou |first1=PE |last2=Mansouri |first2=A |last3=Lebrec |first3=D |last4=Durand |first4=F |last5=Valla |first5=D |last6=Moreau |first6=R |title=Autophagy in liver diseases. |journal=Journal of hepatology |date=2010-12 |volume=53 |issue=6 |pages=1123-34 |doi=10.1016/j.jhep.2010.07.006 |pmid=20810185 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20810185-autophagy-in-liver-diseases/ |accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref>。

*[[精氨酸|精氨酸]]（Arg）是一種半必需氨基酸<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kung |first1=HJ |last2=Changou |first2=CA |last3=Li |first3=CF |last4=Ann |first4=DK |title=Chromatophagy: autophagy goes nuclear and captures broken chromatin during arginine-starvation. |journal=Autophagy |date=2015 |volume=11 |issue=2 |pages=419-21 |doi=10.1080/15548627.2015.1009789 |pmid=25650867 |accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref>，有研究人員首次發現{{le|一般性調控阻遏蛋白質激酶2|Gcn2}}可以介導[[γ-干擾素|干擾素-γ]]，響應因缺乏Arg而引起的牛乳腺上皮細胞自噬<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xia |first1=XJ |last2=Gao |first2=YY |last3=Zhang |first3=J |last4=Wang |first4=L |last5=Zhao |first5=S |last6=Che |first6=YY |last7=Ao |first7=CJ |last8=Yang |first8=HJ |last9=Wang |first9=JQ |last10=Lei |first10=LC |title=Autophagy mediated by arginine depletion activation of the nutrient sensor GCN2 contributes to interferon-γ-induced malignant transformation of primary bovine mammary epithelial cells. |journal=Cell death discovery |date=2016 |volume=2 |pages=15065 |doi=10.1038/cddiscovery.2015.65 |pmid=27551491 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27551491-autophagy-mediated-by-arginine-depletion-activation-of-the-nutrient-sensor-gcn2-contributes-to-interferon-induced-malignant-transformation-of-primary-bovine-mammary-epithelial-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-30}}</ref>。

*[[麩醯胺酸|麩醯胺酸]]（Gln）是人體中含量最豐富的非必需氨基酸。有研究發現通過Gln缺乏的[[培養基|培養基]]處理豬腸道上皮細胞8小時後，細胞數目會顯著減少，同時顯著提升LC3-Ⅱ的表達，故而缺乏Gln會令豬腸道上皮細胞發生自噬<ref>朱玉華;薛欣合;周天驕等.谷氨酰胺、精氨酸和亮氨酸缺乏誘導豬腸道上皮細胞自噬的研究.中國畜牧獸醫學會動物營養學分會第十一次全國動物營養學術研討會論文集.長沙:中國畜牧獸醫學會,2012.</ref>。

===窄譜中波紫外線===
窄譜中波紫外線（NB⁃UVB）可以促進正常[[黑素細胞|黑素細胞]]發生自噬，使用[[穿透式電子顯微鏡|穿透式電子顯微鏡]]觀察有關細胞時，發現隨著NB⁃UVB照射劑量的增大，黑素細胞中的黑素小體會增多，而細胞質內出現較多單層膜空泡狀的自噬溶酶體，以及較少的雙層膜自噬體。有研究人員結合他們的研究結果及以往的研究報道，推測NB⁃UVB通過上調黑素細胞自噬水平的途徑，促進黑素細胞存活，並且可以在[[白癜風|白癜風]]治療中發揮作用<ref>{{cite journal |author1=王敏 |author2=耿清偉 |author3=高亞麗 |author4=華優 |author5=宋秀祖 |title=窄譜中波紫外線對體外培養人黑素细胞自噬水平的影响 |journal=中華皮膚科雜誌 |date=2018 |volume=51 |issue=9 |doi=10.3760/cma.j.issn.0412-4030.2018.09.007 |accessdate=2020-02-02}}</ref>。

===懸浮粒子===
2013年，首次報道暴露於PM2.5可以提高[[A549細胞|A549細胞]]內的活性氧簇生成，並且促進自噬激活及抑制細胞成活，呈[[濃度|濃度]]和[[時間|時間]]依賴性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deng |first1=X |last2=Zhang |first2=F |last3=Rui |first3=W |last4=Long |first4=F |last5=Wang |first5=L |last6=Feng |first6=Z |last7=Chen |first7=D |last8=Ding |first8=W |title=PM2.5-induced oxidative stress triggers autophagy in human lung epithelial A549 cells. |journal=Toxicology in vitro : an international journal published in association with BIBRA |date=2013-09 |volume=27 |issue=6 |pages=1762-70 |doi=10.1016/j.tiv.2013.05.004 |pmid=23685237 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23685237-pm25-induced-oxidative-stress-triggers-autophagy-in-human-lung-epithelial-a549-cells/ |accessdate=2020-02-02}}</ref>。2014年，有研究證實暴露於PM2.5不僅可以通過死亡受體途徑和線粒體途徑誘導A549細胞凋亡，同時可以誘導A549細胞發生自噬性細胞死亡，並且發現二者存在交互作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deng |first1=X |last2=Zhang |first2=F |last3=Wang |first3=L |last4=Rui |first4=W |last5=Long |first5=F |last6=Zhao |first6=Y |last7=Chen |first7=D |last8=Ding |first8=W |title=Airborne fine particulate matter induces multiple cell death pathways in human lung epithelial cells. |journal=Apoptosis : an international journal on programmed cell death |date=2014-07 |volume=19 |issue=7 |pages=1099-112 |doi=10.1007/s10495-014-0980-5 |pmid=24722831 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24722831-airborne-fine-particulate-matter-induces-multiple-cell-death-pathways-in-human-lung-epithelial-cells/ |accessdate=2020-02-02}}</ref>。2015年，有研究發現，PM2.5通過AMPK的信號通路，誘導產生自噬體及表達自噬相關蛋白，通過mTOR信號通路抑制細胞自噬，而與MAPK信號通路沒有明顯的相關性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=Y |last2=Lin |first2=Z |last3=Huang |first3=H |last4=He |first4=H |last5=Yang |first5=L |last6=Chen |first6=T |last7=Yang |first7=T |last8=Ren |first8=N |last9=Jiang |first9=Y |last10=Xu |first10=W |last11=Kamp |first11=DW |last12=Liu |first12=T |last13=Liu |first13=G |title=AMPK is required for PM2.5-induced autophagy in human lung epithelial A549 cells. |journal=International journal of clinical and experimental medicine |date=2015 |volume=8 |issue=1 |pages=58-72 |pmid=25784975 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4358430/ |accessdate=2020-02-02}}</ref>。進一步的研究更顯示，暴露於高劑量PM2.5可以促進人類肺上皮細胞BEAS-2B的自噬功能障礙<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zhou |first1=W |last2=Yuan |first2=X |last3=Zhang |first3=L |last4=Su |first4=B |last5=Tian |first5=D |last6=Li |first6=Y |last7=Zhao |first7=J |last8=Wang |first8=Y |last9=Peng |first9=S |title=Overexpression of HO-1 assisted PM2.5-induced apoptosis failure and autophagy-related cell necrosis. |journal=Ecotoxicology and environmental safety |date=2017-11 |volume=145 |pages=605-614 |doi=10.1016/j.ecoenv.2017.07.047 |pmid=28802142 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28802142-overexpression-of-ho-1-assisted-pm25-induced-apoptosis-failure-and-autophagy-related-cell-necrosis/ |accessdate=2020-02-02}}</ref>。

==和運動之關聯==
自噬對於基礎的[[體內平衡|體內平衡]]至關重要，並且在運動過程中保持肌肉穩定狀態也非常重要<ref name=He2012>{{cite journal | vauthors = He C, Bassik MC, Moresi V, Sun K, Wei Y, Zou Z, An Z, Loh J, Fisher J, Sun Q, Korsmeyer S, Packer M, May HI, Hill JA, Virgin HW, Gilpin C, Xiao G, Bassel-Duby R, Scherer PE, Levine B | title = Exercise-induced BCL2-regulated autophagy is required for muscle glucose homeostasis | journal = Nature | volume = 481 | issue = 7382 | pages = 511–5 | date = January 2012 | pmid = 22258505 | pmc = 3518436 | doi = 10.1038/nature10758 | displayauthors = etal | bibcode = 2012Natur.481..511H }}</ref><ref name=Klionsky2011>{{cite journal | vauthors = Nair U, Klionsky DJ | title = Activation of autophagy is required for muscle homeostasis during physical exercise | journal = Autophagy | volume = 7 | issue = 12 | pages = 1405–6 | date = December 2011 | pmid = 22082869 | pmc = 3288013 | doi = 10.4161/auto.7.12.18315 }}</ref>。對小鼠的研究表明，自噬對於不斷變化的營養和能量需求至關重要，特別是通過蛋白質進行分解代謝的代謝途徑。2012年，由{{le|德克薩斯大學達拉斯西南醫學中心|University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center}}進行的一項研究中，測試了具有{{le|BCL2|Bcl-2}}磷酸化位點突變的小鼠驗證此理論。實驗結果顯示，這些小鼠在急性運動中，表現出耐力下降和葡萄糖代謝改變的情況<ref name=He2012/>。另一項則研究表明，膠原蛋白VI基因敲除小鼠的骨骼肌纖維因自噬作用不足而顯示變性的跡象，導致線粒體受損和細胞死亡<ref name=Grumati11>{{cite journal | vauthors = Grumati P, Coletto L, Schiavinato A, Castagnaro S, Bertaggia E, Sandri M, Bonaldo P | title = Physical exercise stimulates autophagy in normal skeletal muscles but is detrimental for collagen VI-deficient muscles | journal = Autophagy | volume = 7 | issue = 12 | pages = 1415–23 | date = December 2011 | pmid = 22024752 | pmc = 3288016 | doi = 10.4161/auto.7.12.17877 }}</ref> 。運動誘導的自噬未能成功，然而在運動後以人為的方式進行自噬作用時，可以防止受損的細胞器在缺乏{{le|膠原蛋白VI|Collagen VI}}的肌肉纖維中積累，並且保持細胞穩態。兩項研究均表明自噬可能有助於運動的有益代謝作用，並且在維持運動過程中的肌肉穩態，尤其是在膠原VI纖維中至關重要<ref name=He2012/><ref name=Klionsky2011/><ref name=Grumati11/>。波恩大學細胞生物學研究所的研究表明，收縮肌肉會誘發{{le|伴侶-輔助選擇性自噬|Chaperone-assisted selective autophagy}}（CASA），CASA是在機械張力下維持肌肉肌節必需的<ref name="pmid20060297">{{cite journal | vauthors = Arndt V, Dick N, Tawo R, Dreiseidler M, Wenzel D, Hesse M, Fürst DO, Saftig P, Saint R, Fleischmann BK, Hoch M, Höhfeld J | title = Chaperone-assisted selective autophagy is essential for muscle maintenance | journal = Current Biology | volume = 20 | issue = 2 | pages = 143–8 | date = January 2010 | pmid = 20060297 | pmc = | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2009.11.022 }}</ref>。CASA分子伴侶複合物識別機械損傷的[[細胞骨架|細胞骨架]]成分，並且通過蛋白依賴性自噬途徑，將這些細胞骨架成分引導至溶酶體進行處理。這是維持肌肉活動必需的<ref name="pmid20060297" /><ref name="pmid23434281">{{cite journal | vauthors = Ulbricht A, Eppler FJ, Tapia VE, van der Ven PF, Hampe N, Hersch N, Vakeel P, Stadel D, Haas A, Saftig P, Behrends C, Fürst DO, Volkmer R, Hoffmann B, Kolanus W, Höhfeld J | title = Cellular mechanotransduction relies on tension-induced and chaperone-assisted autophagy | journal = Current Biology | volume = 23 | issue = 5 | pages = 430–5 | date = March 2013 | pmid = 23434281 | pmc = | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2013.01.064 }}</ref>。

==炎症與自噬之間的相互作用==
自噬調節劑控制炎症調節劑，反之亦然<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Cadwell | first1 = K | title = Crosstalk between autophagy and inflammatory signalling pathways: balancing defence and homeostasis. | journal = Nature | date = 2016 | pmid = 27694913 | pmc = 5343289 | doi = 10.1038/nri.2016.100 | volume = 16 | issue = 11 | pages = 661–675}}</ref>。脊椎動物細胞通常會激活炎症，以增強免疫系統處理感染的能力，並且啟動恢復組織結構和功能的過程<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Medzhitov | first1 = R | title = Origin and physiological roles of inflammation. | journal = Nature | date = 2008 | pmid = 18650913 | doi = 10.1038/nature07201 | volume = 454 | issue = 7203 | pages = 428–435}}</ref> ，故而至關重要的是將去除細胞和[[細菌|細菌]]碎片的機制與調節炎症的主要因素結合起來：溶酶體在自噬過程中對細胞成分的降解，可以回收重要的分子，並且產生及積聚物質來幫助細胞應對不斷變化的微環境<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Tan | first1 = P | title = Autophagy and Immune-Related Diseases. | journal = Adv Exp Med Biol | date = 2019 | pmid = 31728870 | doi = 10.1007/978-981-15-0606-2_10 | volume = 1209 | pages = 167–179| series = Advances in Experimental Medicine and Biology | isbn = 978-981-15-0605-5 }}</ref>。控制炎症和自噬的蛋白質形成了一個對組織功能至關重要的網絡，而該網絡在癌症中失調：在癌細胞中，異常表達及突變的蛋白質增加細胞存活，對保護惡性細胞的蛋白水解系統「重新連接」網絡的依賴性<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Varisli | first1 = L | title = Dissecting pharmacological effects of Chloroquine in cancer treatment: interference with inflammatory signaling pathways. | journal = Immunology | date = 2019 | pmid = 31782148 | doi = 10.1111/imm.13160}}</ref>。這使癌細胞容易受到自噬調節劑的干預。

