===骨關節炎===
由於自噬隨著年齡的增長而下降，是[[骨關節炎|骨關節炎]]的主要危險因素，因此自噬在該疾病發展中的作用得到重視。在人類和小鼠的關節軟骨中，參與自噬的蛋白質都隨著年齡的增長而減少<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Caramés B, Taniguchi N, Otsuki S, Blanco FJ, Lotz M | title = Autophagy is a protective mechanism in normal cartilage, and its aging-related loss is linked with cell death and osteoarthritis | journal = Arthritis and Rheumatism | volume = 62 | issue = 3 | pages = 791–801 | date = March 2010 | pmid = 20187128 | pmc = 2838960 | doi = 10.1002/art.27305 }}</ref>。經培養的軟骨外植體，其機械損傷也會減少自噬蛋白<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Caramés B, Taniguchi N, Seino D, Blanco FJ, D'Lima D, Lotz M | title = Mechanical injury suppresses autophagy regulators and pharmacologic activation of autophagy results in chondroprotection | journal = Arthritis and Rheumatism | volume = 64 | issue = 4 | pages = 1182–92 | date = April 2012 | pmid = 22034068 | pmc = 3288456 | doi = 10.1002/art.33444 }}</ref>。自噬在正常的軟骨中會不斷被激活，但會隨著[[年齡|年齡]]的增長而受到損害，並且先於軟骨細胞死亡和出現結構受到破壞的現象<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Caramés B, Olmer M, Kiosses WB, Lotz MK | title = The relationship of autophagy defects to cartilage damage during joint aging in a mouse model | journal = Arthritis & Rheumatology | volume = 67 | issue = 6 | pages = 1568–76 | date = June 2015 | pmid = 25708836 | pmc = 4446178 | doi = 10.1002/art.39073 }}</ref>。因此，自噬參與了關節的正常保護過程。

===炎症性腸病===
[[炎症性腸病|炎症性腸病]]（inflammatory bowel disease）是由易感基因、環境和免疫系統之間一系列的相互作用所導致的慢性且易復發的[[消化系統|消化系統]]疾病，包括[[潰瘍性結腸炎|潰瘍性結腸炎]]和[[克隆氏症|克隆氏症]]等。功能失調的自噬被認為是炎症性腸病的發病因素。臨床上廣泛使用的炎症性腸病治療劑與自噬均密切相關，均能誘導細胞自噬的發生，包括[[類固醇|類固醇]]、[[美沙拉嗪|5-氨基水楊酸]]及[[硫唑嘌呤|硫銼嘌呤]]等<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Iida |first1=T |last2=Onodera |first2=K |last3=Nakase |first3=H |title=Role of autophagy in the pathogenesis of inflammatory bowel disease. |journal=World journal of gastroenterology |date=2017-03-21 |volume=23 |issue=11 |pages=1944-1953 |doi=10.3748/wjg.v23.i11.1944 |pmid=28373760 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5360635/#__ffn_sectitle |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。[[尼古丁|尼古丁]]目前已被用作潰瘍性結腸炎患者的治療劑<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lunney |first1=PC |last2=Leong |first2=RW |title=Review article: Ulcerative colitis, smoking and nicotine therapy. |journal=Alimentary pharmacology & therapeutics |date=2012-12 |volume=36 |issue=11-12 |pages=997-1008 |doi=10.1111/apt.12086 |pmid=23072629 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23072629-review-article-ulcerative-colitis-smoking-and-nicotine-therapy/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>，咀嚼尼古丁口香糖可以有效控制輕度及中度結腸炎的病症<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Berkowitz |first1=L |last2=Schultz |first2=BM |last3=Salazar |first3=GA |last4=Pardo-Roa |first4=C |last5=Sebastián |first5=VP |last6=Álvarez-Lobos |first6=MM |last7=Bueno |first7=SM |title=Impact of Cigarette Smoking on the Gastrointestinal Tract Inflammation: Opposing Effects in Crohn's Disease and Ulcerative Colitis. |journal=Frontiers in immunology |date=2018 |volume=9 |pages=74 |doi=10.3389/fimmu.2018.00074 |pmid=29441064 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29441064-impact-of-cigarette-smoking-on-the-gastrointestinal-tract-inflammation-opposing-effects-in-crohns-disease-and-ulcerative-colitis/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。經尼古丁處理後，細胞內雙層自噬泡及自噬小體的數量明顯增高。尼古丁誘導自噬的分子機制可能與內質網應激相關，或者可能與mTOR信號通路相關<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wong |first1=MK |last2=Holloway |first2=AC |last3=Hardy |first3=DB |title=Nicotine Directly Induces Endoplasmic Reticulum Stress Response in Rat Placental Trophoblast Giant Cells. |journal=Toxicological sciences : an official journal of the Society of Toxicology |date=2016-05 |volume=151 |issue=1 |pages=23-34 |doi=10.1093/toxsci/kfw019 |pmid=26803847 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26803847-nicotine-directly-induces-endoplasmic-reticulum-stress-response-in-rat-placental-trophoblast-giant-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Guan |first1=Y |last2=Zhang |first2=L |last3=Li |first3=X |last4=Zhang |first4=X |last5=Liu |first5=S |last6=Gao |first6=N |last7=Li |first7=L |last8=Gao |first8=G |last9=Wei |first9=G |last10=Chen |first10=Z |last11=Zheng |first11=Y |last12=Ma |first12=X |last13=Siwko |first13=S |last14=Chen |first14=JL |last15=Liu |first15=M |last16=Li |first16=D |title=Repression of Mammalian Target of Rapamycin Complex 1 Inhibits Intestinal Regeneration in Acute Inflammatory Bowel Disease Models. |journal=Journal of immunology (Baltimore, Md. : 1950) |date=2015-07-01 |volume=195 |issue=1 |pages=339-46 |doi=10.4049/jimmunol.1303356 |pmid=26026060 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26026060-repression-of-mammalian-target-of-rapamycin-complex-1-inhibits-intestinal-regeneration-in-acute-inflammatory-bowel-disease-models/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。目前已有不少研究證實尼古丁與內質網應激存在密切關係，因為他們發現尼古丁上調GRP78/BIP的表達水平，並且直接誘導內質網應激，上調內質網應激標誌物PERK、{{le|EIF2A|EIF2A}}等的表達或[[磷酸化|磷酸化]]修飾。對低[[濃度|濃度]]尼古丁的研究有助於開發調節自噬治療潰瘍性結腸炎的新治療靶點。

===牙周炎===
自噬能促進感染細胞對病原體和毒素的清除，抵抗細菌的入侵。然而，{{le|牙齦卟啉單胞菌|Porphyromonas gingivalis}}等牙周細菌則可逃避自噬分子的識別，干擾自噬體形成，阻止自噬體和溶酶體融合，甚至可以在自噬體中生存和增殖，利用其中的蛋白質等物質為自身生存提供[[能量|能量]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bélanger |first1=M |last2=Rodrigues |first2=PH |last3=Dunn WA |first3=Jr |last4=Progulske-Fox |first4=A |title=Autophagy: a highway for Porphyromonas gingivalis in endothelial cells. |journal=Autophagy |date=NaN |volume=2 |issue=3 |pages=165-70 |doi=10.4161/auto.2828 |pmid=16874051 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16874051-autophagy-a-highway-for-porphyromonas-gingivalis-in-endothelial-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。目前的研究雖提示自噬與[[牙周炎|牙周炎]]相關，但沒有充分的證據證實自噬在牙周炎中的作用是保護作用還是病理作用。因為有研究發現牙周炎[[患者|患者]]相較於健康人群的[[外周血|外周血]][[單核細胞|單核細胞]]中，自噬基因表達量更高，而自噬作用被抑制後，出現了細胞存活率降低及凋亡細胞比例增加的情況，表明自噬在牙周炎中的保護作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Levine |first1=B |last2=Klionsky |first2=DJ |title=Development by self-digestion: molecular mechanisms and biological functions of autophagy. |journal=Developmental cell |date=2004-04 |volume=6 |issue=4 |pages=463-77 |doi=10.1016/s1534-5807(04)00099-1 |pmid=15068787 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15068787-development-by-self-digestion-molecular-mechanisms-and-biological-functions-of-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。然而，有研究得出相反的結果，表明自噬在牙周炎中的病理作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Tsuda |first1=H |last2=Ochiai |first2=K |last3=Suzuki |first3=N |last4=Otsuka |first4=K |title=Butyrate, a bacterial metabolite, induces apoptosis and autophagic cell death in gingival epithelial cells. |journal=Journal of periodontal research |date=2010-10 |volume=45 |issue=5 |pages=626-34 |doi=10.1111/j.1600-0765.2010.01277.x |pmid=20546110 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20546110-butyrate-a-bacterial-metabolite-induces-apoptosis-and-autophagic-cell-death-in-gingival-epithelial-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。

===敗血症及其併發症===
[[敗血症|敗血症]]是感染誘導的失調性宿主免疫反應。目前已知自噬在敗血症進展與器官功能障礙的發生中具有一定保護作用，故而是一個值得研究的治療靶點。大量促炎因子及聚集的[[白細胞|白細胞]]通過炎症信號通路，誘導組織細胞內出現內質網應激及線粒體損傷等，繼而誘發保護性自噬反應，以包裹損傷的細胞器，限制損傷信號的擴散<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lewis |first1=AJ |last2=Billiar |first2=TR |last3=Rosengart |first3=MR |title=Biology and Metabolism of Sepsis: Innate Immunity, Bioenergetics, and Autophagy. |journal=Surgical infections |date=2016-06 |volume=17 |issue=3 |pages=286-93 |doi=10.1089/sur.2015.262 |pmid=27093228 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27093228-biology-and-metabolism-of-sepsis-innate-immunity-bioenergetics-and-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。敗血症時，[[肝|肝]]細胞代謝狀態會出現改變，肝細胞通過自噬來分解胞內有機物，並且產生小分子，以維持代謝需要，而分解的產物（例如[[糖類|糖類]]、[[脂類|脂類]]及氨基酸等）又可有負反饋的作用，減弱自噬作用的程度<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Madrigal-Matute |first1=J |last2=Cuervo |first2=AM |title=Regulation of Liver Metabolism by Autophagy. |journal=Gastroenterology |date=2016-02 |volume=150 |issue=2 |pages=328-39 |doi=10.1053/j.gastro.2015.09.042 |pmid=26453774 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26453774-regulation-of-liver-metabolism-by-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。由於[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]能夠增強肺部組織的自噬水平，所以有學者發表了了關於吸入低濃度一氧化碳，以治療敗血症引致的肺部損傷的報道<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hoetzel |first1=A |last2=Dolinay |first2=T |last3=Schmidt |first3=R |last4=Choi |first4=AM |last5=Ryter |first5=SW |title=Carbon monoxide in sepsis. |journal=Antioxidants & redox signaling |date=2007-11 |volume=9 |issue=11 |pages=2013-26 |doi=10.1089/ars.2007.1762 |pmid=17822362 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17822362-carbon-monoxide-in-sepsis/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

===結核病===
自噬参与到宿主细胞清除胞内致病菌的免疫应答中。[[結核桿菌|結核分枝桿菌]]是一种胞内寄生菌，目前發現自噬有利於清除結核桿菌<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chen |first1=S |last2=Yuan |first2=J |last3=Yao |first3=S |last4=Jin |first4=Y |last5=Chen |first5=G |last6=Tian |first6=W |last7=Xi |first7=J |last8=Xu |first8=Z |last9=Weng |first9=D |last10=Chen |first10=J |title=Lipopolysaccharides may aggravate apoptosis through accumulation of autophagosomes in alveolar macrophages of human silicosis. |journal=Autophagy |date=2015 |volume=11 |issue=12 |pages=2346-57 |doi=10.1080/15548627.2015.1109765 |pmid=26553601 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26553601-lipopolysaccharides-may-aggravate-apoptosis-through-accumulation-of-autophagosomes-in-alveolar-macrophages-of-human-silicosis/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。

在结核的免疫应答中，[[γ-干扰素|γ-干扰素]]不仅可直接加速巨噬细胞通过MHC-Ⅱ呈递抗原的作用；还可调控巨噬细胞表达''[[IRGM|IRGM]]''，继而促进巨噬细胞内产生大量的自噬体，启动巨噬细胞的自噬作用。基因型分析发现，''IRGM''的某些基因型与分支杆菌的易感性明显相关，提示了''IRGM''基因在抗结核自噬中起到关键性作用。

除此之外，自噬也参与获得性免疫，例如加工抗原并通过MHC-Ⅱ的呈递。与此同时，一些結核桿菌的亚群也会进化出一些机制阻碍宿主细胞对其的自噬作用，达到免疫逃避的效果；有些结核杆菌可通过募集并聚合肌动蛋白以逃避泛肽化；而另一些结核杆菌则“丢卒保帅”的策略，主动脱去被泛肽化的细胞壁；这些策略都能使结核杆菌达到从吞噬体中逃离的效果。

自噬可以增強一線抗結核藥物，例如[[異煙肼|異煙肼]]和[[吡嗪酰胺|吡嗪酰胺]]的作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kim |first1=JJ |last2=Lee |first2=HM |last3=Shin |first3=DM |last4=Kim |first4=W |last5=Yuk |first5=JM |last6=Jin |first6=HS |last7=Lee |first7=SH |last8=Cha |first8=GH |last9=Kim |first9=JM |last10=Lee |first10=ZW |last11=Shin |first11=SJ |last12=Yoo |first12=H |last13=Park |first13=YK |last14=Park |first14=JB |last15=Chung |first15=J |last16=Yoshimori |first16=T |last17=Jo |first17=EK |title=Host cell autophagy activated by antibiotics is required for their effective antimycobacterial drug action. |journal=Cell host & microbe |date=2012-05-17 |volume=11 |issue=5 |pages=457-68 |doi=10.1016/j.chom.2012.03.008 |pmid=22607799 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22607799-host-cell-autophagy-activated-by-antibiotics-is-required-for-their-effective-antimycobacterial-drug-action/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。

===癌症===
當調節細胞分化的幾種不同途徑被干擾時，通常會發生癌症。自噬在癌症中起著重要作用，既可以預防癌症，也可以促進癌症的發展<ref name=Furuya>Furuya, N., Liang, X.H., and Levin, B. 2004. Autophagy and cancer. In Autophagy. D.J. Klionsky editor. Landes Bioscience. Georgetown, Texas, USA. 244-253.</ref>。自噬可通過促進已飢餓或通過自噬降解凋亡介體的腫瘤細胞的存活，促進癌症的發展。自噬在癌症中的作用已得到高度研究和審查，目前已知自噬既是腫瘤抑制因子，又是腫瘤細胞存活的因素，然而根據幾種模型，自噬更可能被用作抑癌劑。在自噬的後期階段使用[[氯喹|氯喹]]等抑製劑，會增加被抗腫瘤藥殺死的癌細胞數量<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Vlahopoulos S, Critselis E, Voutsas IF, Perez SA, Moschovi M, Baxevanis CN, Chrousos GP | title = New use for old drugs? Prospective targets of chloroquines in cancer therapy | journal = Current Drug Targets | volume = 383 | issue = 16 | pages = 1564-1576 | date = 2014 | pmid = 25023646 | doi = 10.2174/1389450115666140714121514 }}</ref>。
但是對於自噬作用和癌症的因果關係，以目前的研究結果顯示，尚未明瞭，有可能是自噬基因的突變造成癌症，也可能為癌症使得自噬基因的突變，或甚至互為因果關係，還有待後續研究。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mizushima N, Levine B | title = Autophagy in Human Diseases | journal = The New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 383 | issue = 16 | pages = 1564-1576 | date = 2020 | pmid = 33053285 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMra2022774 }}</ref>。

*'''抑癌藥'''：目前已經對小鼠和{{le|Beclin1|BECN1}}（一種調節自噬的蛋白質）進行了一些實驗。當Beclin1基因變為雜合子時，研究人員發現小鼠體內更容易出現腫瘤<ref name=Qu>{{cite journal | vauthors = Qu X, Yu J, Bhagat G, Furuya N, Hibshoosh H, Troxel A, Rosen J, Eskelinen EL, Mizushima N, Ohsumi Y, Cattoretti G, Levine B | title = Promotion of tumorigenesis by heterozygous disruption of the beclin 1 autophagy gene | journal = The Journal of Clinical Investigation | volume = 112 | issue = 12 | pages = 1809–20 | date = December 2003 | pmid = 14638851 | pmc = 297002 | doi = 10.1172/JCI20039 | displayauthors = etal }}</ref>。然而，當Beclin1過度表達時，腫瘤的發展就會受到抑制<ref name=Liang>{{cite journal | vauthors = Liang XH, Jackson S, Seaman M, Brown K, Kempkes B, Hibshoosh H, Levine B | title = Induction of autophagy and inhibition of tumorigenesis by beclin 1 | journal = Nature | volume = 402 | issue = 6762 | pages = 672–6 | date = December 1999 | pmid = 10604474 | doi = 10.1038/45257 | displayauthors = etal | bibcode = 1999Natur.402..672L }}</ref> 。在解釋beclin突變體的[[表型|表型]]，並且將觀察結果歸因於自噬存在缺陷時應該要格外小心。Beclin1通常是產生{{le|磷脂酰肌醇3-磷酸|Phosphatidylinositol 3-phosphate}}的必需物質，因此它會影響許多溶酶體和內體功能，包括內吞作用和已活化的內吞降解生長因子受體。有認為Beclin1存在着通過非依賴自噬的途徑，影響癌症發展的可能性，然而事實是Atg7或Atg5等的核心自噬因子（暫時未知會影響其他細胞進程，並且不影響細胞增殖和細胞死亡）敲除各個基因時，顯示出非常不同的表型。此外，Beclin1的完全[[基因敲落|基因敲落]]會對胚胎致死，而Atg7或Atg5的敲落對則胚胎無害。壞死和慢性炎症也已顯示出通過自噬而受到限制，有助於防止腫瘤細胞的形成<ref name=Duran>{{cite journal | vauthors = Duran A, Linares JF, Galvez AS, Wikenheiser K, Flores JM, Diaz-Meco MT, Moscat J | title = The signaling adaptor p62 is an important NF-kappaB mediator in tumorigenesis | journal = Cancer Cell | volume = 13 | issue = 4 | pages = 343–54 | date = April 2008 | pmid = 18394557 | doi = 10.1016/j.ccr.2008.02.001 | displayauthors = etal }}</ref>。

*'''腫瘤細胞存活率'''：自噬在腫瘤細胞存活中發揮重要作用。在癌細胞中，自噬被用作一種應對細胞壓力的途徑<ref name=Paglin>{{cite journal | vauthors = Paglin S, Hollister T, Delohery T, Hackett N, McMahill M, Sphicas E, Domingo D, Yahalom J | title = A novel response of cancer cells to radiation involves autophagy and formation of acidic vesicles | journal = Cancer Research | volume = 61 | issue = 2 | pages = 439–44 | date = January 2001 | pmid = 11212227 }}</ref>。例如，miRNA-4673誘導自噬是一種有助癌細胞生存的機制，可以提高癌細胞對放射線的抵抗力<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Dökümcü K, Simonian M, Farahani RM | title = miR4673 improves fitness profile of neoplastic cells by induction of autophagy | journal = Cell Death & Disease | volume = 9 | issue = 11 | pages = 1068 | date = October 2018 | pmid = 30341280 | pmc = 6195512 | doi = 10.1038/s41419-018-1088-6 }}</ref> 。一旦這些自噬相關基因被抑制，細胞死亡的情況就會加劇<ref name=Jin>{{cite journal | vauthors = Jin S, White E | title = Role of autophagy in cancer: management of metabolic stress | journal = Autophagy | volume = 3 | issue = 1 | pages = 28–31 | year = 2007 | pmid = 16969128 | pmc = 2770734 | doi = 10.4161/auto.3269 }}</ref>。自噬抵消了代謝能的增加。這些代謝壓力包括缺氧、營養缺乏及細胞增殖增加。這些壓力激活自噬，以回收ATP並維持癌細胞的存活<ref name=Yang>{{cite journal | vauthors = Yang ZJ, Chee CE, Huang S, Sinicrope FA | title = The role of autophagy in cancer: therapeutic implications | journal = Molecular Cancer Therapeutics | volume = 10 | issue = 9 | pages = 1533–41 | date = September 2011 | pmid = 21878654 | doi = 10.1158/1535-7163.MCT-11-0047 | pmc = 3170456 }}</ref>。自噬已被證明可以通過維持細胞[[能量|能量]]的產生，而使腫瘤細胞持續地生長。通過[[抑制|抑制]]這些腫瘤細胞中的自噬基因，發現腫瘤消退，並且延長了受腫瘤影響的器官的存活率。此外，也顯示出抑制自噬可以增強抗癌治療的效果<ref name=Yang/> 。

*'''細胞死亡機制'''：承受極大壓力的細胞會通過[[細胞凋亡|細胞凋亡]]或[[壞死|壞死]]經歷細胞死亡。長時間的自噬激活會導致[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]和細胞器的高轉換率。高於生存閾值的比率，可能會殺死具有高凋亡閾值的癌細胞<ref name=Yang/><ref name=":0">{{cite journal | vauthors = Tavassoly I, Parmar J, Shajahan-Haq AN, Clarke R, Baumann WT, Tyson JJ | title = Dynamic Modeling of the Interaction Between Autophagy and Apoptosis in Mammalian Cells | journal = CPT | volume = 4 | issue = 4 | pages = 263–72 | date = April 2015 | pmid = 26225250 | pmc = 4429580 | doi = 10.1002/psp4.29 }}</ref>。該技術可以用作癌症的治療方法。

*'''治療目標'''：有研究發現，靶向自噬可能是抗擊癌症的可行治療方法。自噬在腫瘤抑制和腫瘤細胞存活中均起作用。因此，自噬可以用作預防癌症的策略。第一種策略是誘導自噬並增強其腫瘤抑制特性。第二種策略是抑制自噬，從而誘導細胞凋亡<ref name="Jin"/>。通過研究自噬誘導療法期間的劑量反應抗腫瘤作用，測試了第一種策略。這些療法表明自噬以劑量依賴性方式增加。 這也直接與癌細胞的生長呈劑量依賴性<ref name=Paglin/><ref name=":0"/>。該數據支持將鼓勵自噬的療法的發展。其次，抑制直接誘導自噬的蛋白質途徑也可以用作抗癌治療<ref name="Jin"/><ref name=":0"/>。第二種策略發現自噬是用於維持體內穩態的蛋白質降解系統，並且發現抑制自噬通常會導致細胞凋亡。抑制自噬的風險較高，因為可能導致細胞存活，而不是預計中的細胞死亡<ref name=Paglin/>。

*'''自噬的負調節物'''：{{le|mTOR|mTOR}}，{{le|CFLAR|CFLAR}}和[[表皮生長因子受體|表皮生長因子受體]]等自噬的負調節物，被安排在自噬級聯反應的不同階段發揮作用。自噬消化的最終產物也可以充當負反饋調節機制，以阻止長時間的活動<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Razaghi A, Heimann K, Schaeffer PM, Gibson SB | title = Negative regulators of cell death pathways in cancer: perspective on biomarkers and targeted therapies | journal = Apoptosis | volume = 23 | issue = 2 | pages = 93–112 | date = February 2018 | pmid = 29322476 | doi = 10.1007/s10495-018-1440-4 }}</ref>。

===柏金遜症===
[[File:Autophagy.jpg|thumb]]

[[柏金遜症|柏金遜症]]是一種[[神經退化障礙|神經退化性疾病]]，可以肇因於黑質{{le|緻密部|Pars compacta}}的多巴胺性神經元退化。柏金遜症的特徵是在受影響的[[神經元|神經元]]中，包含着細胞無法分解的{{le|α-突觸核蛋白|Alpha-synuclein}}，其以{{le|路易氏體|Lewy body}}的形式堆積，故而柏金遜症被視為一種突觸核蛋白病變。自噬途徑的失調和調節自噬的等位基因的突變被認為會引起神經退化性疾​​病。自噬對神經元的生存至關重要。如果沒有有效的自噬作用，神經元會聚集遍在蛋白化的蛋白質聚集體並降解。蛋白質是已被泛素標記以降解的蛋白質。突觸核蛋白等位基因的突變導致溶酶體pH值升高和水解酶抑制。由實驗結果可知，溶酶體降解能力降低。該疾病涉及多種基因突變，包括功能喪失{{le|PTEN誘導激酶-1|PINK1}}<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Valente EM, Abou-Sleiman PM, Caputo V, Muqit MM, Harvey K, Gispert S, Ali Z, Del Turco D, Bentivoglio AR, Healy DG, Albanese A, Nussbaum R, González-Maldonado R, Deller T, Salvi S, Cortelli P, Gilks WP, Latchman DS, Harvey RJ, Dallapiccola B, Auburger G, Wood NW | title = Hereditary early-onset Parkinson's disease caused by mutations in PINK1 | journal = Science | volume = 304 | issue = 5674 | pages = 1158–60 | date = May 2004 | pmid = 15087508 | doi = 10.1126/science.1096284 | bibcode = 2004Sci...304.1158V }}</ref>和Parkin<ref name = "Kitada_1998">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kitada T, Asakawa S, Hattori N, Matsumine H, Yamamura Y, Minoshima S, Yokochi M, Mizuno Y, Shimizu N | title = Mutations in the parkin gene cause autosomal recessive juvenile parkinsonism | journal = Nature | volume = 392 | issue = 6676 | pages = 605–8 | date = April 1998 | pmid = 9560156 | doi = 10.1038/33416 | bibcode = 1998Natur.392..605K }}</ref> 。這些基因的功能喪失可能導致線粒體積累和蛋白質聚集體受損，而不是導致細胞變性。線粒體參與柏金遜症。在特發性帕金森氏病中，該病通常是由線粒體功能異常、細胞氧化應激、自噬作用的改變和蛋白質聚集引起的，並會導致線粒體腫脹和去極化<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Esteves AR, Arduíno DM, Silva DF, Oliveira CR, Cardoso SM | title = Mitochondrial Dysfunction: The Road to Alpha-Synuclein Oligomerization in PD | journal = Parkinson's Disease | volume = 2011 | issue = | pages = 693761 | date = January 2011 | pmid = 21318163 | pmc = 3026982 | doi = 10.4061/2011/693761 }}</ref>。

===阿茲海默症===
[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]是一種普遍流行於老年群體，並且以記憶、行為及學習功能障礙為主要特徵的神經退行性疾病<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Alzheimer’s |first1=Association. |title=2015 Alzheimer's disease facts and figures. |journal=Alzheimer's & dementia : the journal of the Alzheimer's Association |date=2015-03 |volume=11 |issue=3 |pages=332-84 |doi=10.1016/j.jalz.2015.02.003 |pmid=25984581 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25984581-2015-alzheimers-disease-facts-and-figures/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。自噬作用的異常是導致阿茲海默症的兩大神經病理改變，即瀰漫於整個大腦皮層的β 澱粉樣蛋白（Aβ）老年斑的形成，以及[[神經元|神經元]][[細胞核|細胞核]]周圍堆積的無膜束狀異常纖維[[包涵體|包涵體]]（主要由過度磷酸化[[Tau蛋白|Tau蛋白]]組成）的重要原因<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Dronse |first1=J |last2=Fliessbach |first2=K |last3=Bischof |first3=GN |last4=von Reutern |first4=B |last5=Faber |first5=J |last6=Hammes |first6=J |last7=Kuhnert |first7=G |last8=Neumaier |first8=B |last9=Onur |first9=OA |last10=Kukolja |first10=J |last11=van Eimeren |first11=T |last12=Jessen |first12=F |last13=Fink |first13=GR |last14=Klockgether |first14=T |last15=Drzezga |first15=A |title=In vivo Patterns of Tau Pathology, Amyloid-β Burden, and Neuronal Dysfunction in Clinical Variants of Alzheimer's Disease. |journal=Journal of Alzheimer's disease : JAD |date=2017 |volume=55 |issue=2 |pages=465-471 |doi=10.3233/JAD-160316 |pmid=27802224 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27802224-in-vivo-patterns-of-tau-pathology-amyloid-burden-and-neuronal-dysfunction-in-clinical-variants-of-alzheimers-disease/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。此時的Tau蛋白失去促進微管組裝的生物學活性，並且表現出抗蛋白水解酶的神經毒性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ml |first1=Steinhilb |last2=D |first2=Dias-Santagata |last3=Ta |first3=Fulga |last4=Dl |first4=Felch |last5=Mb |first5=Feany |title=Tau Phosphorylation Sites Work in Concert to Promote Neurotoxicity in Vivo |journal=Molecular biology of the cell |date=2007-12 |volume=18 |issue=12 |pmid=17928404 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17928404-tau-phosphorylation-sites-work-in-concert-to-promote-neurotoxicity-in-vivo/ |accessdate=2020-01-25 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mocanu |first1=MM |last2=Nissen |first2=A |last3=Eckermann |first3=K |last4=Khlistunova |first4=I |last5=Biernat |first5=J |last6=Drexler |first6=D |last7=Petrova |first7=O |last8=Schönig |first8=K |last9=Bujard |first9=H |last10=Mandelkow |first10=E |last11=Zhou |first11=L |last12=Rune |first12=G |last13=Mandelkow |first13=EM |title=The potential for beta-structure in the repeat domain of tau protein determines aggregation, synaptic decay, neuronal loss, and coassembly with endogenous Tau in inducible mouse models of tauopathy. |journal=The Journal of neuroscience : the official journal of the Society for Neuroscience |date=2008-01-16 |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=737-48 |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.2824-07.2008 |pmid=18199773 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18199773-the-potential-for-beta-structure-in-the-repeat-domain-of-tau-protein-determines-aggregation-synaptic-decay-neuronal-loss-and-coassembly-with-endogenous-tau-in-inducible-mouse-models-of-tauopathy/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。細胞[[囊泡|囊泡]]在正常情況下，通過溶酶體途徑的代謝速率很高，故而產生的Aβ量很少，不會造成Aβ的堆積，然而自噬體轉運異常或溶酶體對自噬體內容物降解效率下降，會導致自噬體堆積、大量Aβ及老年斑的形成。Tau蛋白的兩大代謝途徑是自噬-溶酶體和泛素-蛋白體酶體系統<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lee |first1=MJ |last2=Lee |first2=JH |last3=Rubinsztein |first3=DC |title=Tau degradation: the ubiquitin-proteasome system versus the autophagy-lysosome system. |journal=Progress in neurobiology |date=2013-06 |volume=105 |pages=49-59 |doi=10.1016/j.pneurobio.2013.03.001 |pmid=23528736 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23528736-tau-degradation-the-ubiquitin-proteasome-system-versus-the-autophagy-lysosome-system/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>，並且是在自噬受體NDP52的協助下進行清除。自噬作用參與過度表達Tau蛋白和異常磷酸化Tau蛋白的降解，可以降低[[磷酸化|磷酸化]]Tau蛋白寡聚體的水平，不過對內源性Tau蛋白則没有明顯影響，並且發現抑制自噬作用能夠增加Tau蛋白的[[細胞毒性|細胞毒性]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chesser |first1=AS |last2=Ganeshan |first2=V |last3=Yang |first3=J |last4=Johnson |first4=GV |title=Epigallocatechin-3-gallate enhances clearance of phosphorylated tau in primary neurons. |journal=Nutritional neuroscience |date=2016 |volume=19 |issue=1 |pages=21-31 |doi=10.1179/1476830515Y.0000000038 |pmid=26207957 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26207957-epigallocatechin-3-gallate-enhances-clearance-of-phosphorylated-tau-in-primary-neurons/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Caccamo |first1=A |last2=Magrì |first2=A |last3=Medina |first3=DX |last4=Wisely |first4=EV |last5=López-Aranda |first5=MF |last6=Silva |first6=AJ |last7=Oddo |first7=S |title=mTOR regulates tau phosphorylation and degradation: implications for Alzheimer's disease and other tauopathies. |journal=Aging cell |date=2013-06 |volume=12 |issue=3 |pages=370-80 |doi=10.1111/acel.12057 |pmid=23425014 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23425014-mtor-regulates-tau-phosphorylation-and-degradation-implications-for-alzheimers-disease-and-other-tauopathies/ |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>。自噬在阿茲海默症中的作用具有兩面性。在阿茲海默症早期，由蛋白質損傷和聚集等因素誘發的自噬可以發揮保護作用。如果長[[時間|時間]]維持這種狀態，或者溶酶體功能出現異常，就會形成[[神經元|神經元]]萎縮及細胞死亡等病理改變，所以自噬的平衡十分重要<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Cherra SJ |first1=3rd |last2=Chu |first2=CT |title=Autophagy in neuroprotection and neurodegeneration: A question of balance. |journal=Future neurology |date=2008-05 |volume=3 |issue=3 |pages=309-323 |doi=10.2217/14796708.3.3.309 |pmid=18806889 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2544613/#__ffn_sectitle |accessdate=2020-01-28}}</ref>。

===青光眼===
[[青光眼|青光眼]]是一種以{{le|視網膜神經節細胞|Retinal ganglion cell}}（RGCs）和[[視神經|視神經]][[軸突|軸突]]的逐漸喪失為特徵的神經退行性疾病，並且伴有視野敏感性的喪失<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=Y |last2=Xu |first2=K |last3=Zhang |first3=H |last4=Zhao |first4=J |last5=Zhu |first5=X |last6=Wang |first6=Y |last7=Wu |first7=R |title=Retinal ganglion cell death is triggered by paraptosis via reactive oxygen species production: a brief literature review presenting a novel hypothesis in glaucoma pathology. |journal=Molecular medicine reports |date=2014-09 |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=1179-83 |doi=10.3892/mmr.2014.2346 |pmid=24969312 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24969312-retinal-ganglion-cell-death-is-triggered-by-paraptosis-via-reactive-oxygen-species-production-a-brief-literature-review-presenting-a-novel-hypothesis-in-glaucoma-pathology/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。目前已知自噬在青光眼的發生中起着重要的作用，並且因為大量的動物實驗研究指出自噬的激活導致RGCs的凋亡，故而抑制自噬可能是預防青光眼RGCs變性的一個臨床靶點，所以有學者寄望自噬靶向治療能夠成為青光眼視神經退行性疾病的一種治療方法<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rodríguez-Muela |first1=N |last2=Germain |first2=F |last3=Mariño |first3=G |last4=Fitze |first4=PS |last5=Boya |first5=P |title=Autophagy promotes survival of retinal ganglion cells after optic nerve axotomy in mice. |journal=Cell death and differentiation |date=2012-01 |volume=19 |issue=1 |pages=162-9 |doi=10.1038/cdd.2011.88 |pmid=21701497 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21701497-autophagy-promotes-survival-of-retinal-ganglion-cells-after-optic-nerve-axotomy-in-mice/ |accessdate=2020-01-25}}</ref>。

===病毒方面===
自噬作為[[真核生物|真核細胞]]早期的保護防禦機制，可以清除{{le|水疱性口炎病毒|Indiana vesiculovirus}}（VSV）等病原體，例如VSV的複製過程可被自噬有效抑制。然而，[[克沙奇病毒|克沙奇病毒]]B3（CVB3）、[[丙型肝炎|丙型肝炎]]病毒（HCV）、[[流行性乙型腦炎|乙型腦炎病毒]]（JEV）等病毒具有快速[[進化|進化]]以應對宿主細胞免疫作用的能力<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Randow |first1=F |last2=Münz |first2=C |title=Autophagy in the regulation of pathogen replication and adaptive immunity. |journal=Trends in immunology |date=2012-10 |volume=33 |issue=10 |pages=475-87 |doi=10.1016/j.it.2012.06.003 |pmid=22796170 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22796170-autophagy-in-the-regulation-of-pathogen-replication-and-adaptive-immunity/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>，甚至會利用自噬來增強病毒的增殖<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Pei |first1=J |last2=Zhao |first2=M |last3=Ye |first3=Z |last4=Gou |first4=H |last5=Wang |first5=J |last6=Yi |first6=L |last7=Dong |first7=X |last8=Liu |first8=W |last9=Luo |first9=Y |last10=Liao |first10=M |last11=Chen |first11=J |title=Autophagy enhances the replication of classical swine fever virus in vitro. |journal=Autophagy |date=2014-01 |volume=10 |issue=1 |pages=93-110 |doi=10.4161/auto.26843 |pmid=24262968 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24262968-autophagy-enhances-the-replication-of-classical-swine-fever-virus-in-vitro/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=G |last2=Yu |first2=Y |last3=Tu |first3=Y |last4=Tong |first4=J |last5=Liu |first5=Y |last6=Zhang |first6=C |last7=Chang |first7=Y |last8=Wang |first8=S |last9=Jiang |first9=C |last10=Zhou |first10=EM |last11=Cai |first11=X |title=Highly Pathogenic Porcine Reproductive and Respiratory Syndrome Virus Infection Induced Apoptosis and Autophagy in Thymi of Infected Piglets. |journal=PloS one |date=2015 |volume=10 |issue=6 |pages=e0128292 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0128292 |pmid=26046751 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26046751-highly-pathogenic-porcine-reproductive-and-respiratory-syndrome-virus-infection-induced-apoptosis-and-autophagy-in-thymi-of-infected-piglets/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Meng |first1=C |last2=Zhou |first2=Z |last3=Jiang |first3=K |last4=Yu |first4=S |last5=Jia |first5=L |last6=Wu |first6=Y |last7=Liu |first7=Y |last8=Meng |first8=S |last9=Ding |first9=C |title=Newcastle disease virus triggers autophagy in U251 glioma cells to enhance virus replication. |journal=Archives of virology |date=2012-06 |volume=157 |issue=6 |pages=1011-8 |doi=10.1007/s00705-012-1270-6 |pmid=22398914 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22398914-newcastle-disease-virus-triggers-autophagy-in-u251-glioma-cells-to-enhance-virus-replication/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Datan |first1=E |last2=Roy |first2=SG |last3=Germain |first3=G |last4=Zali |first4=N |last5=McLean |first5=JE |last6=Golshan |first6=G |last7=Harbajan |first7=S |last8=Lockshin |first8=RA |last9=Zakeri |first9=Z |title=Dengue-induced autophagy, virus replication and protection from cell death require ER stress (PERK) pathway activation. |journal=Cell death & disease |date=2016-03-03 |volume=7 |pages=e2127 |doi=10.1038/cddis.2015.409 |pmid=26938301 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26938301-dengue-induced-autophagy-virus-replication-and-protection-from-cell-death-require-er-stress-perk-pathway-activation/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。在自噬被激活後，乙肝病毒<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sir |first1=D |last2=Tian |first2=Y |last3=Chen |first3=WL |last4=Ann |first4=DK |last5=Yen |first5=TS |last6=Ou |first6=JH |title=The early autophagic pathway is activated by hepatitis B virus and required for viral DNA replication. |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America |date=2010-03-02 |volume=107 |issue=9 |pages=4383-8 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0911373107 |pmid=20142477 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20142477-the-early-autophagic-pathway-is-activated-by-hepatitis-b-virus-and-required-for-viral-dna-replication/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>及丙肝病毒<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ke |first1=PY |last2=Chen |first2=SS |title=Activation of the unfolded protein response and autophagy after hepatitis C virus infection suppresses innate antiviral immunity in vitro. |journal=The Journal of clinical investigation |date=2011-01 |volume=121 |issue=1 |pages=37-56 |doi=10.1172/JCI41474 |pmid=21135505 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21135505-activation-of-the-unfolded-protein-response-and-autophagy-after-hepatitis-c-virus-infection-suppresses-innate-antiviral-immunity-in-vitro/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>會對自噬體的降解產生抑製作用。HPIV 3病毒會抑制自噬体及溶酶體的融合，阻止自噬體的降解，從而提高病毒的增殖<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Levine |first1=B |last2=Mizushima |first2=N |last3=Virgin |first3=HW |title=Autophagy in immunity and inflammation. |journal=Nature |date=2011-01-20 |volume=469 |issue=7330 |pages=323-35 |doi=10.1038/nature09782 |pmid=21248839 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21248839-autophagy-in-immunity-and-inflammation/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。{{le|T細胞白血病|T-cell leukemia}}通過{{le|Tax蛋白|Tax gene product}}阻斷自噬小體與溶酶體的融合，增加自噬小體的積累，並且促進病毒的複製<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Tang |first1=SW |last2=Chen |first2=CY |last3=Klase |first3=Z |last4=Zane |first4=L |last5=Jeang |first5=KT |title=The cellular autophagy pathway modulates human T-cell leukemia virus type 1 replication. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-virology_2013-02_87_3/page/1699 |journal=Journal of virology |date=2013-02 |volume=87 |issue=3 |pages=1699-707 |doi=10.1128/JVI.02147-12 |pmid=23175371 |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ren |first1=T |last2=Takahashi |first2=Y |last3=Liu |first3=X |last4=Loughran |first4=TP |last5=Sun |first5=SC |last6=Wang |first6=HG |last7=Cheng |first7=H |title=HTLV-1 Tax deregulates autophagy by recruiting autophagic molecules into lipid raft microdomains. |journal=Oncogene |date=2015-01-15 |volume=34 |issue=3 |pages=334-45 |doi=10.1038/onc.2013.552 |pmid=24362528 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24362528-htlv-1-tax-deregulates-autophagy-by-recruiting-autophagic-molecules-into-lipid-raft-microdomains/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。有關[[脊髓灰質炎|脊髓灰質炎]]病毒的研究指出，當自噬體與質膜融合時，自噬體內的病毒[[離子|離子]]被釋放<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deretic |first1=V |last2=Levine |first2=B |title=Autophagy balances inflammation in innate immunity. |journal=Autophagy |date=2018 |volume=14 |issue=2 |pages=243-251 |doi=10.1080/15548627.2017.1402992 |pmid=29165043 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29165043-autophagy-balances-inflammation-in-innate-immunity/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。

===性傳播疾病方面===
目前有研究指出自噬在[[性傳播疾病|性傳播疾病]]病原體的在進入宿主細胞後可以激活自噬，但是又可以逃避或抑制自噬，故而針對有關作用機制的研究或能幫助性傳播疾病的治療和預後，以及新型[[藥物|藥物]]與[[疫苗|疫苗]]的研發。許多自噬相關基因都是人類免疫缺陷病毒-1感染依賴因子<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Brass |first1=AL |last2=Dykxhoorn |first2=DM |last3=Benita |first3=Y |last4=Yan |first4=N |last5=Engelman |first5=A |last6=Xavier |first6=RJ |last7=Lieberman |first7=J |last8=Elledge |first8=SJ |title=Identification of host proteins required for HIV infection through a functional genomic screen. |journal=Science (New York, N.Y.) |date=2008-02-15 |volume=319 |issue=5865 |pages=921-6 |doi=10.1126/science.1152725 |pmid=18187620 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18187620-identification-of-host-proteins-required-for-hiv-infection-through-a-functional-genomic-screen/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>，故而HIV-1的早期複製依賴於自噬。HIV-1許多的病毒蛋白可以透過抑制自噬過程的方式，而在宿主體內持續性複製存活。例如{{le|Env|Env (基因)}}編碼的外膜蛋白{{le|gp120|Envelope glycoprotein GP120}}<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Espert |first1=L |last2=Denizot |first2=M |last3=Grimaldi |first3=M |last4=Robert-Hebmann |first4=V |last5=Gay |first5=B |last6=Varbanov |first6=M |last7=Codogno |first7=P |last8=Biard-Piechaczyk |first8=M |title=Autophagy is involved in T cell death after binding of HIV-1 envelope proteins to CXCR4. |journal=The Journal of clinical investigation |date=2006-08 |volume=116 |issue=8 |pages=2161-72 |doi=10.1172/JCI26185 |pmid=16886061 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16886061-autophagy-is-involved-in-t-cell-death-after-binding-of-hiv-1-envelope-proteins-to-cxcr4/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>、反式激活因子{{le|Tat|Tat (HIV)}}<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sagnier |first1=S |last2=Daussy |first2=CF |last3=Borel |first3=S |last4=Robert-Hebmann |first4=V |last5=Faure |first5=M |last6=Blanchet |first6=FP |last7=Beaumelle |first7=B |last8=Biard-Piechaczyk |first8=M |last9=Espert |first9=L |title=Autophagy restricts HIV-1 infection by selectively degrading Tat in CD4+ T lymphocytes. |journal=Journal of virology |date=2015-01 |volume=89 |issue=1 |pages=615-25 |doi=10.1128/JVI.02174-14 |pmid=25339774 |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>及負性因子調控蛋白[[Nef|Nef]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Campbell |first1=GR |last2=Rawat |first2=P |last3=Bruckman |first3=RS |last4=Spector |first4=SA |title=Human Immunodeficiency Virus Type 1 Nef Inhibits Autophagy through Transcription Factor EB Sequestration. |journal=PLoS pathogens |date=2015-06 |volume=11 |issue=6 |pages=e1005018 |doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1005018 |pmid=26115100 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26115100-human-immunodeficiency-virus-type-1-nef-inhibits-autophagy-through-transcription-factor-eb-sequestration/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>等。[[淋球菌|淋球菌]]可以抑制自噬流，增強淋球菌在[[巨噬細胞|巨噬細胞]]中的存活能力<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zughaier |first1=SM |last2=Kandler |first2=JL |last3=Balthazar |first3=JT |last4=Shafer |first4=WM |title=Phosphoethanolamine Modification of Neisseria gonorrhoeae Lipid A Reduces Autophagy Flux in Macrophages. |journal=PloS one |date=2015 |volume=10 |issue=12 |pages=e0144347 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0144347 |pmid=26641098 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26641098-phosphoethanolamine-modification-of-neisseria-gonorrhoeae-lipid-a-reduces-autophagy-flux-in-macrophages/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>，也可以阻礙自噬小體成熟及自噬小體與溶酶體的融合過程，以逃避自噬介導的殺傷作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kim |first1=WJ |last2=Mai |first2=A |last3=Weyand |first3=NJ |last4=Rendón |first4=MA |last5=Van Doorslaer |first5=K |last6=So |first6=M |title=Neisseria gonorrhoeae evades autophagic killing by downregulating CD46-cyt1 and remodeling lysosomes. |journal=PLoS pathogens |date=2019-02 |volume=15 |issue=2 |pages=e1007495 |doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1007495 |pmid=30753248 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30753248-neisseria-gonorrhoeae-evades-autophagic-killing-by-downregulating-cd46-cyt1-and-remodeling-lysosomes/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lu |first1=P |last2=Wang |first2=S |last3=Lu |first3=Y |last4=Neculai |first4=D |last5=Sun |first5=Q |last6=van der Veen |first6=S |title=A Subpopulation of Intracellular Neisseria gonorrhoeae Escapes Autophagy-Mediated Killing Inside Epithelial Cells. |journal=The Journal of infectious diseases |date=2019-01-01 |volume=219 |issue=1 |pages=133-144 |doi=10.1093/infdis/jiy237 |pmid=29688440 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29688440-a-subpopulation-of-intracellular-neisseria-gonorrhoeae-escapes-autophagy-mediated-killing-inside-epithelial-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。[[砂眼衣原體|砂眼衣原體]]抑制細胞內溶酶體酶的活性，阻礙晚期自噬小體與自噬小體與溶酶體的融合過程，導致自噬的完整性受到抑制，降低自噬的抗感染作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Al-Younes |first1=HM |last2=Brinkmann |first2=V |last3=Meyer |first3=TF |title=Interaction of Chlamydia trachomatis serovar L2 with the host autophagic pathway. |journal=Infection and immunity |date=2004-08 |volume=72 |issue=8 |pages=4751-62 |doi=10.1128/IAI.72.8.4751-4762.2004 |pmid=15271937 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15271937-interaction-of-chlamydia-trachomatis-serovar-l2-with-the-host-autophagic-pathway/ |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。除此之外，高危型HPV調節細胞內[[小分子核糖核酸|小分子核糖核酸]]的水平，影響自噬過程。例如miR-224-3p的高表達減少FIP200（參與自噬小體形成的蛋白）的水平，因抑制宿主細胞自噬而促進[[子宮頸癌|子宮頸癌]]的進展<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fang |first1=W |last2=Shu |first2=S |last3=Yongmei |first3=L |last4=Endong |first4=Z |last5=Lirong |first5=Y |last6=Bei |first6=S |title=miR-224-3p inhibits autophagy in cervical cancer cells by targeting FIP200. |journal=Scientific reports |date=2016-09-12 |volume=6 |pages=33229 |doi=10.1038/srep33229 |pmid=27615604 |accessdate=2020-01-27}}</ref>。

===不育症===
自噬在精子發生過程中起着重要作用。精原幹細胞中的缺失或受損可引起不可逆性的弱精子症及無精子症等，導致不育症<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Tegelenbosch |first1=RA |last2=de Rooij |first2=DG |title=A quantitative study of spermatogonial multiplication and stem cell renewal in the C3H/101 F1 hybrid mouse. |journal=Mutation research |date=1993-12 |volume=290 |issue=2 |pages=193-200 |doi=10.1016/0027-5107(93)90159-d |pmid=7694110 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7694110-a-quantitative-study-of-spermatogonial-multiplication-and-stem-cell-renewal-in-the-c3h101-f1-hybrid-mouse/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。當遇精原幹細胞到不利環境時，會為了適應代謝條件的變化而進行細胞自噬調節。例如，有研究指出三鄰甲苯基磷酸酯等生殖毒性物質均可使大鼠精原幹細胞的自噬標誌蛋白及LC3-II/LC3-I 比明顯增加，細胞內含有大量退化細胞器的自噬泡顯著增加<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Liu |first1=ML |last2=Wang |first2=JL |last3=Wei |first3=J |last4=Xu |first4=LL |last5=Yu |first5=M |last6=Liu |first6=XM |last7=Ruan |first7=WL |last8=Chen |first8=JX |title=Tri-ortho-cresyl phosphate induces autophagy of rat spermatogonial stem cells. |journal=Reproduction (Cambridge, England) |date=2015-02 |volume=149 |issue=2 |pages=163-70 |doi=10.1530/REP-14-0446 |pmid=25385720 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25385720-tri-ortho-cresyl-phosphate-induces-autophagy-of-rat-spermatogonial-stem-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xu |first1=LL |last2=Liu |first2=ML |last3=Wang |first3=JL |last4=Yu |first4=M |last5=Chen |first5=JX |title=Saligenin cyclic-o-tolyl phosphate (SCOTP) induces autophagy of rat spermatogonial stem cells. |journal=Reproductive toxicology (Elmsford, N.Y.) |date=2016-04 |volume=60 |pages=62-8 |doi=10.1016/j.reprotox.2016.01.004 |pmid=26815770 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26815770-saligenin-cyclic-o-tolyl-phosphate-scotp-induces-autophagy-of-rat-spermatogonial-stem-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。而且，精原幹細胞中的自噬作用可以清除錯誤折疊蛋白質，以及受損細胞器，故而對細胞起著保護作用。此外，自噬作用可以促進減數分裂前DNA複製，既為細胞提供[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]及[[核苷酸|核苷酸]]等<ref>{{cite journal |last1=McNally |first1=K |last2=Berg |first2=E |last3=Cortes |first3=DB |last4=Hernandez |first4=V |last5=Mains |first5=PE |last6=McNally |first6=FJ |title=Katanin maintains meiotic metaphase chromosome alignment and spindle structure in vivo and has multiple effects on microtubules in vitro. |journal=Molecular biology of the cell |date=2014-04 |volume=25 |issue=7 |pages=1037-49 |doi=10.1091/mbc.E13-12-0764 |pmid=24501424 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3967969/#!po=81.0345 |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kabeya |first1=Y |last2=Mizushima |first2=N |last3=Ueno |first3=T |last4=Yamamoto |first4=A |last5=Kirisako |first5=T |last6=Noda |first6=T |last7=Kominami |first7=E |last8=Ohsumi |first8=Y |last9=Yoshimori |first9=T |title=LC3, a mammalian homologue of yeast Apg8p, is localized in autophagosome membranes after processing. |journal=The EMBO journal |date=2000-11-01 |volume=19 |issue=21 |pages=5720-8 |doi=10.1093/emboj/19.21.5720 |pmid=11060023 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC305793/#!po=80.1370 |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>，也保證基因遺傳的穩定性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gallardo Bolaños |first1=JM |last2=Miró Morán |first2=Á |last3=Balao da Silva |first3=CM |last4=Morillo Rodríguez |first4=A |last5=Plaza Dávila |first5=M |last6=Aparicio |first6=IM |last7=Tapia |first7=JA |last8=Ortega Ferrusola |first8=C |last9=Peña |first9=FJ |title=Autophagy and apoptosis have a role in the survival or death of stallion spermatozoa during conservation in refrigeration. |journal=PloS one |date=2012 |volume=7 |issue=1 |pages=e30688 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0030688 |pmid=22292020 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3266901/#!po=69.2771 |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。PDLIM1蛋白是一種精子細胞骨架組裝的負調控因子，並且是通過自噬途徑而降解，以維持微管結構的組裝<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zhuo |first1=C |last2=Ji |first2=Y |last3=Chen |first3=Z |last4=Kitazato |first4=K |last5=Xiang |first5=Y |last6=Zhong |first6=M |last7=Wang |first7=Q |last8=Pei |first8=Y |last9=Ju |first9=H |last10=Wang |first10=Y |title=Proteomics analysis of autophagy-deficient Atg7-/- MEFs reveals a close relationship between F-actin and autophagy. |journal=Biochemical and biophysical research communications |date=2013-08-02 |volume=437 |issue=3 |pages=482-8 |doi=10.1016/j.bbrc.2013.06.111 |pmid=23850690 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23850690-proteomics-analysis-of-autophagy-deficient-atg7-mefs-reveals-a-close-relationship-between-f-actin-and-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。這對精子形成有著重要作用。然而，有研究指出高脂肪食物可誘導小鼠體內的自噬作用被過度激活，導致精子生成存在缺陷<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mu |first1=Y |last2=Yan |first2=WJ |last3=Yin |first3=TL |last4=Zhang |first4=Y |last5=Li |first5=J |last6=Yang |first6=J |title=Diet-induced obesity impairs spermatogenesis: a potential role for autophagy. |journal=Scientific reports |date=2017-03-09 |volume=7 |pages=43475 |doi=10.1038/srep43475 |pmid=28276438 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28276438-diet-induced-obesity-impairs-spermatogenesis-a-potential-role-for-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-23}}</ref>。

===抑鬱症===
自噬可能參與[[抑鬱症|抑鬱症]]的發生<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Abelaira |first1=HM |last2=Réus |first2=GZ |last3=Neotti |first3=MV |last4=Quevedo |first4=J |title=The role of mTOR in depression and antidepressant responses. |journal=Life sciences |date=2014-04-17 |volume=101 |issue=1-2 |pages=10-4 |doi=10.1016/j.lfs.2014.02.014 |pmid=24582593 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24582593-the-role-of-mtor-in-depression-and-antidepressant-responses/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，有多個證據提示細胞自噬的異常可能參與抑鬱症的發生<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Polajnar |first1=M |last2=Zerovnik |first2=E |title=Impaired autophagy: a link between neurodegenerative and neuropsychiatric diseases. |journal=Journal of cellular and molecular medicine |date=2014-09 |volume=18 |issue=9 |pages=1705-11 |doi=10.1111/jcmm.12349 |pmid=25139375 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25139375-impaired-autophagy-a-link-between-neurodegenerative-and-neuropsychiatric-diseases/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，例如有研究指出{{le|精神分裂症斷裂基因1|DISC1}}（一種精神疾病的關鍵易感基因）能被自噬途徑降解<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Atkin |first1=TA |last2=Brandon |first2=NJ |last3=Kittler |first3=JT |title=Disrupted in Schizophrenia 1 forms pathological aggresomes that disrupt its function in intracellular transport. |journal=Human molecular genetics |date=2012-05-01 |volume=21 |issue=9 |pages=2017-28 |doi=10.1093/hmg/dds018 |pmid=22291444 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22291444-disrupted-in-schizophrenia-1-forms-pathological-aggresomes-that-disrupt-its-function-in-intracellular-transport/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>、躁狂抑鬱症患者血清中蛋白激酶B（AKT）和mTOR [[信使核糖核酸|信使核糖核酸]]水平下降<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Machado-Vieira |first1=R |last2=Zanetti |first2=MV |last3=Teixeira |first3=AL |last4=Uno |first4=M |last5=Valiengo |first5=LL |last6=Soeiro-de-Souza |first6=MG |last7=Oba-Shinjo |first7=SM |last8=de Sousa |first8=RT |last9=Zarate CA |first9=Jr |last10=Gattaz |first10=WF |last11=Marie |first11=SK |title=Decreased AKT1/mTOR pathway mRNA expression in short-term bipolar disorder. |journal=European neuropsychopharmacology : the journal of the European College of Neuropsychopharmacology |date=2015-04 |volume=25 |issue=4 |pages=468-73 |doi=10.1016/j.euroneuro.2015.02.002 |pmid=25726893 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25726893-decreased-akt1mtor-pathway-mrna-expression-in-short-term-bipolar-disorder/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>、雙相抑鬱症患者腦內Bcl-2的水平下降<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kim |first1=HW |last2=Rapoport |first2=SI |last3=Rao |first3=JS |title=Altered expression of apoptotic factors and synaptic markers in postmortem brain from bipolar disorder patients. |journal=Neurobiology of disease |date=2010-03 |volume=37 |issue=3 |pages=596-603 |doi=10.1016/j.nbd.2009.11.010 |pmid=19945534 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19945534-altered-expression-of-apoptotic-factors-and-synaptic-markers-in-postmortem-brain-from-bipolar-disorder-patients/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，已知Bcl-2是通過與Beclin-1結合從而抑制自噬的發生。自噬對抑鬱症等神經系統疾病的調節作用是正向，抑或負向仍然存有爭議<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Son |first1=JH |last2=Shim |first2=JH |last3=Kim |first3=KH |last4=Ha |first4=JY |last5=Han |first5=JY |title=Neuronal autophagy and neurodegenerative diseases. |journal=Experimental & molecular medicine |date=2012-02-29 |volume=44 |issue=2 |pages=89-98 |doi=10.3858/emm.2012.44.2.031 |pmid=22257884 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22257884-neuronal-autophagy-and-neurodegenerative-diseases/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>。有研究提示激活自噬能促進[[突觸|突觸]]的發展<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Shen |first1=W |last2=Ganetzky |first2=B |title=Autophagy promotes synapse development in Drosophila. |journal=The Journal of cell biology |date=2009-10-05 |volume=187 |issue=1 |pages=71-9 |doi=10.1083/jcb.200907109 |pmid=19786572 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19786572-autophagy-promotes-synapse-development-in-drosophila/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，另一些研究則證實抗抑鬱藥可以通過抑制自噬，發揮抗抑鬱的作用。

===作為藥物靶標===
由於自噬失調與多種疾病的發病機理有關，因此科研人員投入了許多努力來鑑定和表徵可以調節自噬的合成人工合成小分子或天然小分子<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Moosavi |first1=MA |last2=Haghi |first2=A |last3=Rahmati |first3=M |last4=Taniguchi |first4=H |last5=Mocan |first5=A |last6=Echeverría |first6=J |last7=Gupta |first7=VK |last8=Tzvetkov |first8=NT |last9=Atanasov |first9=AG |title=Phytochemicals as potent modulators of autophagy for cancer therapy. |journal=Cancer letters |date=2018-06-28 |volume=424 |pages=46-69 |doi=10.1016/j.canlet.2018.02.030 |pmid=29474859 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29474859-phytochemicals-as-potent-modulators-of-autophagy-for-cancer-therapy/ |accessdate=2020-01-21}}</ref>。

例如，巨噬细胞的自噬作用可消灭结核杆菌，对结核病治愈有益。研究人员通过小鼠实验发现，从[[东革阿里|东革阿里]]中提取的巴沙克布明A可诱导巨噬细胞自噬从而控制结核杆菌的增殖<ref>Hyo-Ji, Lee, Hyun-Jeong, et al. Pasakbumin A controls the growth of Mycobacterium tuberculosis by enhancing the autophagy and production of antibacterial mediators in mouse macrophages.[J]. PloS one, 2019.</ref>。

以神經退化性疾病來說，增強自噬作用是非常有展望，但需要擔憂的就是目前的藥物都是依賴於溶體活性，但在此類疾病中，溶體往往已經有功能上缺失了，因此可能對於藥物的作用就沒預期那麼好，所以需要警慎選擇目標疾病和階段才可以使藥物有最大的作用效果。
目前自噬調節療法都非選擇性、非特定在自噬作用上，像是mTORC1抑制劑，會抑制其他多種代謝途徑；甚至某些藥物可能同時具有誘導自噬作用和抑制自噬作用。
因此未來在藥物標靶研究上，應該專於在特定自噬作用過程上，避免有影響其他細胞生理機能的情況。

==檢測方法==
第一是LC3 turnover實驗，因為單檢測LC3-II的靜態水平並不能夠完全反映細胞內的自噬潮變化，故而需要聯合自噬後期抑制劑如溶酶體抑制劑Bafilomycin A1或CQ，來比較LC3-II在抑制劑加入前後的變化差異。第二是[[綠色螢光蛋白|綠色螢光蛋白]]（GFP）的抗降解性，通過檢測[[轉染|轉染]]了GFP-LC3的細胞所產生的GFP片段來評判細胞內自噬水平的變化。第三是以{{le|p62|Nucleoporin 62}}蛋白作為自噬活性指標，經常被科研人員用作自噬水平升高的輔助檢測手段，然而需聯合其他檢測手段進行證實。第四是mRFP-GFP-LC3雙螢光活細胞成像，實時動態監測自噬過程，並且能夠通過[[顏色|顏色]]變化確定自噬潮[[水平|水平]]的高低。第五是使用[[電子顯微鏡|電子顯微鏡]]，然而對[[實驗|實驗]]設備和實驗者的技能與辨別能力要求較高<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ylä-Anttila |first1=P |last2=Vihinen |first2=H |last3=Jokitalo |first3=E |last4=Eskelinen |first4=EL |title=Monitoring autophagy by electron microscopy in Mammalian cells. |journal=Methods in enzymology |date=2009 |volume=452 |pages=143-64 |doi=10.1016/S0076-6879(08)03610-0 |pmid=19200881 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19200881-monitoring-autophagy-by-electron-microscopy-in-mammalian-cells/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，有學者推薦進行[[雙盲|雙盲]]實驗來定量細胞中自噬體或自噬溶酶體數量。第六是[[流式細胞術|流式細胞術]]，可以檢測各個細胞時相的自噬水平，還可以直接計算出螢光強度和[[陽性|陽性]]細胞[[百分比|百分比]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Eng |first1=KE |last2=Panas |first2=MD |last3=Karlsson Hedestam |first3=GB |last4=McInerney |first4=GM |title=A novel quantitative flow cytometry-based assay for autophagy. |journal=Autophagy |date=2010-07 |volume=6 |issue=5 |pages=634-41 |doi=10.4161/auto.6.5.12112 |pmid=20458170 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20458170-a-novel-quantitative-flow-cytometry-based-assay-for-autophagy/ |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>，然而在細胞在染色之前，需要使用[[防垢劑|去垢劑]]預處理細胞質中的LC3-I。

===影響因素===
第一個主要影響因素是[[培養基|培養基]]的新鮮程度及[[血清|血清]]，防止較高溫度下長時間或不適當存儲而導致的左旋[[麩醯胺酸|麩醯胺酸]]（L-glutamine）降解，並產生[[氨|氨]]。目前已知氨會因影響溶酶體的pH值而對自噬潮有明顯的抑製作用，並且通過抑制mTORC1促進自噬<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Li |first1=Z |last2=Ji |first2=X |last3=Wang |first3=W |last4=Liu |first4=J |last5=Liang |first5=X |last6=Wu |first6=H |last7=Liu |first7=J |last8=Eggert |first8=US |last9=Liu |first9=Q |last10=Zhang |first10=X |title=Ammonia Induces Autophagy through Dopamine Receptor D3 and MTOR. |journal=PloS one |date=2016 |volume=11 |issue=4 |pages=e0153526 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0153526 |pmid=27077655 |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4831814/#__ffn_sectitle |accessdate=2020-01-24}}</ref>。此外，血清也對自噬活性也有顯著影響。第二個主要影響因素是培養基的換液時間，因為培養基換液的目的，就是要減弱培養基及細胞[[代謝|代謝]]產物，對藥物靶點相關信號通路本底產生的影響。

